msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hey..."
msgstr "Ehi..."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Are you sure about this?"
msgstr "Sei sicuro di quello che fai?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I mean, don't you think\r\nit's almost time?"
msgstr "Insomma, non credi\r\nche sia quasi ora?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Nah, he should be fine for now."
msgstr "Nah, per ora dovrebbe stare bene."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I just want to enjoy my drink\r\nfor a little longer."
msgstr "Voglio solo godermi il mio drink\r\nancora per un po'."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You."
msgstr "Tu."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Outside, now, Kiryu."
msgstr "Fuori, ora, Kiryu."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Thought I told ya I don't wanna\r\nsee yer sorry ass in here again."
msgstr "Pensavo di averti detto che non volevo\r\npiù vedere il tuo brutto muso qui dentro."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Could you at least try to be\r\na little polite to my customers?"
msgstr "Potresti almeno cercare di essere\r\nun po' educato con i miei clienti?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "But I been coming 'round yer\r\nplace way longer than this guy!"
msgstr "Ma io vengo nel tuo\r\nlocale da molto più tempo di lui!"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Y'gonna pick him over me?\r\nReally?"
msgstr "Scegli lui al posto mio?\r\nDavvero?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Yer headin' fer\r\na real whoopin' this time."
msgstr "Stavolta ti aspetta\r\nuna bella batosta."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Well!? Get on out there!"
msgstr "Beh!? Vai fuori!"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I ain't lettin' ya ignore me!"
msgstr "Non ti permetto di ignorarmi!"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Hey, Nagumo-kun!"
msgstr "Ehi, Nagumo-kun!"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "O-Oh, uh..."
msgstr "O-Oh, uh..."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I'll pay you back later, 'kay?"
msgstr "Ti pago dopo, ok?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Sorry 'bout that, Kiyo-chan."
msgstr "Scusa per questo, Kiyo-chan."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "I won't be long."
msgstr "Non ci metterò molto."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Like hell you won't."
msgstr "Col cavolo che non ci metterai molto."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna make sure\r\ny'get gone fer good."
msgstr "Mi assicurerò che te ne\r\nvada per sempre."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I'll swing by some other time."
msgstr "Passerò un'altra volta."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "See ya!"
msgstr "Ci vediamo!"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Y'ready to tussle? Huh!?"
msgstr "Sei pronto a lottare? Eh!?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna teach ya good, punks\r\nwho mess with me don't get off easy."
msgstr "Ti darò una bella lezione, i teppistelli\r\nche si mettono contro di me non la passano liscia."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Best start prayin' now."
msgstr "Ti conviene iniziare a pregare."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Truth is, y'just made a fool outta me\r\nin front of the woman I love..."
msgstr "La verità è che mi hai appena fatto fare la figura dell'idiota\r\ndavanti alla donna che amo..."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "How d'ya reckon that feels?"
msgstr "Come pensi che ci si senta?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "The Hiroshima yakuza don't take kindly\r\nt'city slickers like you, y'hear me!?"
msgstr "La yakuza di Hiroshima non è molto gentile\r\ncon i fighetti di città come te, mi hai sentito!?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Givin' me all that high n' mighty bull..."
msgstr "Con tutta quella stronzata da sbruffone..."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr "Ehi."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Whaddya want!?"
msgstr "Che vuoi!?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Can we get this over with?\r\nI'm on a schedule here."
msgstr "Possiamo farla finita?\r\nHo una tabella di marcia da rispettare."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah?\r\nY'really itchin' to die that bad?"
msgstr "Ah sì?\r\nHai così tanta fretta di morire?"

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Just throw your punch if you're going to."
msgstr "Tira il tuo pugno se devi."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "It's really gonna mess things up if I\r\nhave to listen to any more of this hot air."
msgstr "Farai davvero un casino se dovrò\r\nascoltare ancora tutta quest'aria fritta."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Well y'don't gotta worry then."
msgstr "Beh, allora non devi preoccuparti."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Cause startin' now..."
msgstr "Perché a partire da ora..."

msgctxt "1||a01_010||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "...All yer plans are canceled!"
msgstr "...Tutti i tuoi piani sono cancellati!"

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "'Kay, I getcha."
msgstr "Ok, ho capito."

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "But y'know,\r\nthat was only round one."
msgstr "Ma sai,\r\nquello era solo il primo round."

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I was... just warmin' up a bit."
msgstr "Mi stavo... solo scaldando un po'."

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "The real whuppin' starts now."
msgstr "La vera batosta inizia ora."

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "This has already gone on long enough."
msgstr "Questa storia è andata avanti anche troppo."

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I said, I ain't through with ya yet!"
msgstr "Ho detto che non ho ancora finito con te!"

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Give it a rest already."
msgstr "Dacci un taglio."

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I don't have any more time\r\nto waste on this!"
msgstr "Non ho più tempo\r\nda perdere con te!"

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whaddya mean?"
msgstr "Ch-che vuoi dire?"

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "If you want a fight,\r\nyou'll have to find someone else."
msgstr "Se vuoi combattere,\r\ndovrai trovare qualcun altro."

msgctxt "2||a01_020||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Not everyone's as free as you."
msgstr "Non tutti sono liberi come te."

msgctxt "3||a01_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Welcome back."
msgstr "Bentornato."

msgctxt "3||a01_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Thanks. Looks like I just made it."
msgstr "Grazie. Sembra che ce l'abbia appena fatta."

msgctxt "3||a01_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Mhm."
msgstr "Mhm."

msgctxt "3||a01_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Here, Kiryu-san."
msgstr "Ecco, Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "3||a01_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Hi there. Sorry for the wait."
msgstr "Ciao. Scusa per l'attesa."

msgctxt "3||a01_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You can really throw 'em back..."
msgstr "Riesci davvero a buttarteli giù..."

msgctxt "3||a01_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "...Haruto."
msgstr "...Haruto."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "The man who raised me..."
msgstr "L'uomo che mi ha cresciuta..."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "...was once a member of the yakuza."
msgstr "...era un tempo un membro della yakuza."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I know he looks scary to most people..."
msgstr "So che sembra spaventoso per la maggior parte delle persone..."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "...but he always treated me\r\nwith respect and kindness."
msgstr "...ma mi ha sempre trattata\r\ncon rispetto e gentilezza."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Even though he was a bit unconventional,\r\nI could always rely on him."
msgstr "Anche se era un po' anticonvenzionale,\r\npotevo sempre contare su di lui."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I... I think of him like a father.\r\nAnd I love him very much."
msgstr "Io... Lo considero come un padre.\r\nE gli voglio un mondo di bene."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I don't want to keep lying to\r\neveryone like this though."
msgstr "Non voglio continuare a mentire a\r\ntutti in questo modo però."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Not to my fans... and not to myself."
msgstr "Non ai miei fan... e non a me stessa."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "My dream has always been to be a star."
msgstr "Il mio sogno è sempre stato quello di essere una star."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "But there's something I want even more."
msgstr "Ma c'è qualcosa che voglio ancora di più."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "I want to live a happy life with\r\nthe people I hold closest."
msgstr "Voglio vivere una vita felice con\r\nle persone a me più care."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "That's why I can't continue singing."
msgstr "Ecco perché non posso continuare a cantare."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I'm going to be with Kazuma Kiryu.\r\nHe is my family."
msgstr "Andrò a stare con Kazuma Kiryu.\r\nLui è la mia famiglia."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I have to get back...\r\nEveryone is waiting for me..."
msgstr "Devo tornare...\r\nTutti mi stanno aspettando..."

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz? Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr "Zio Kaz? Zio Kaz!"

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Haruka?"
msgstr "Haruka?"

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Hold on, Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr "Resisti, zio Kaz!"

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "A dream... Am I dreaming?"
msgstr "Un sogno... Sto sognando?"

msgctxt "4||a01_040||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "You're not.\r\nI'm really here, with you."
msgstr "Non lo sei.\r\nSono davvero qui, con te."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Haruka-chan."
msgstr "Haruka-chan."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I just spoke to the doctor."
msgstr "Ho appena parlato con il dottore."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san's gonna be okay.\r\nHe'll be on his way home in a few weeks."
msgstr "Kiryu-san starà bene.\r\nTornerà a casa tra un paio di settimane."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I see. Thank you for checking."
msgstr "Capisco. Grazie per aver controllato."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "By the way, you were real smooth up\r\non stage. It's been all over the news."
msgstr "A proposito, sei stata davvero disinvolta sul\r\npalco. È stato su tutti i telegiornali."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "But, I've gotta warn you, this may not\r\nturn out the way you're hoping it will."
msgstr "Ma, devo avvertirti, questo potrebbe non\r\nfinire come speri tu."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "First you have a yakuza-raised idol\r\nannouncing her retirement mid-concert."
msgstr "Prima di tutto hai un idol cresciuta dalla yakuza\r\nche annuncia il suo ritiro in mezzo a un concerto."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Meanwhile, the Tojo Clan and the Omi Alliance\r\nare tearing at each other's throats in the street."
msgstr "Nel frattempo, il Clan Tojo e l'Alleanza Omi\r\nsi stanno scannando per strada."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "If the news is anything to go by, going back to\r\nthe simple life with Kiryu-san could be rough."
msgstr "Se la notizia è indicativa, tornare alla\r\nvita semplice con Kiryu-san potrebbe essere dura."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Might be a while before things quiet down."
msgstr "Potrebbe volerci un po' prima che le cose si calmino."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "I know."
msgstr "Lo so."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Well, not like it's any of my business anyway."
msgstr "Beh, non che siano affari miei comunque."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I have faith in you two."
msgstr "Ho fede in voi due."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "There's nothing you guys couldn't do."
msgstr "Non c'è niente che voi ragazzi non potreste fare."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Right. Thank you for all\r\nthe help, Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Giusto. Grazie per tutto\r\nl'aiuto, Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "That reminds me, will your business\r\nbe okay without you?"
msgstr "Questo mi ricorda, la tua attività\r\nstarà bene senza di te?"

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "With a secretary like mine on the case?\r\nOh, it'll be more than okay."
msgstr "Con una segretaria come la mia sul caso?\r\nOh, andrà più che bene."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "She's capable of running the show on her\r\nown for a bit. Don't sweat it."
msgstr "È capace di gestire lo spettacolo da sola\r\nper un po'. Non preoccuparti."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "What about you, Haruka-chan?"
msgstr "E tu, Haruka-chan?"

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "You two gonna head back to Morning Glory?"
msgstr "Voi due tornerete al Morning Glory?"

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I think so."
msgstr "Sì, credo di sì."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "That orphanage is where we call home,\r\nand those kids are practically family."
msgstr "Quell'orfanotrofio è quello che chiamiamo casa,\r\ne quei bambini sono praticamente famiglia."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "I see. Guess Kamurocho'll be\r\ngetting a bit lonelier then."
msgstr "Capisco. Immagino che Kamurocho diventerà\r\nun po' più solitaria allora."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "What's up, copper? Slow your roll.\r\nYou're gonna spook the patients."
msgstr "Che succede, piedipiatti? Rallenta.\r\nSpaventerai i pazienti."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "He's here for me."
msgstr "È qui per me."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Eh?"

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "They're arrestin' me again.\r\nI still got time to serve."
msgstr "Mi stanno arrestando di nuovo.\r\nHo ancora del tempo da scontare."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Glad your head's in the right place.\r\nMaybe we'll even be lenient."
msgstr "Sono contento che la tua testa sia a posto.\r\nForse saremo anche clementi."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Taiga Saejima. Please come peacefully."
msgstr "Taiga Saejima. Per favore, vieni pacificamente."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Wasn't plannin' on fightin' ya."
msgstr "Non avevo intenzione di combatterti."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Screw this noise. Why's it always gotta\r\ngo down like this with you, bro?"
msgstr "Al diavolo questo rumore. Perché deve sempre\r\nfinire così con te, fratello?"

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "It's all good."
msgstr "Va tutto bene."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "The rest is up to you, bro."
msgstr "Il resto dipende da te, fratello."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "While you guys're busy cleanin' up\r\nthe Tojo Clan's whole mess..."
msgstr "Mentre voi ragazzi siete impegnati a ripulire\r\ntutto il casino del Clan Tojo..."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "...I'm gonna be bored outta\r\nmy mind in a prison cell."
msgstr "...mi annoierò a morte\r\nin una cella di prigione."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "One more thing."
msgstr "Un'altra cosa."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "This is Kazuma Kiryu's room, yes?"
msgstr "Questa è la stanza di Kazuma Kiryu, vero?"

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Eh? What's it matter?"
msgstr "Eh? Che importa?"

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "I'm with the police.\r\nRemain calm, please."
msgstr "Sono con la polizia.\r\nRimanete calmi, per favore."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Eh?"

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu..."
msgstr "Kazuma Kiryu..."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "Under suspicion of assault and\r\ndestruction of private property..."
msgstr "Sotto sospetto di aggressione e\r\ndistruzione di proprietà privata..."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "...is under arrest."
msgstr "...sei in arresto."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "No prob."
msgstr "Nessun problema."

msgctxt "5||a01_045||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san should be healed up soon enough."
msgstr "Kiryu-san dovrebbe guarire abbastanza in fretta."

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "遥ちゃん"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "秋山さん"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "先生に話聞いてきた"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "桐生さんは大丈夫だ\r\n２週間もすれば退院できるってさ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "そうですか\r\nありがとうございます"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "それにしてもさっきのステージじゃ思い切ったね\r\nニュースで何回も流れている"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "ただ　あそこで君が言ったようにはいかないかもしれない"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "元ヤクザに育てられたアイドルのステージでの引退宣言"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "その周辺で起きていた東城会や近江連合の抗争"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "テレビの騒ぎでわかってるだろうけど\r\n君と桐生さんが一緒に暮らすには覚悟がいるよ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "まわりが静かになるまで少し時間がかかる"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "ええ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "まあ俺なんかが外野から口出す話じゃないか"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "君らなら　きっと大丈夫"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "乗り越えられるさ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "はい　秋山さんには本当にいろいろ助けてもらって"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "そういえばお仕事の方はいいんですか？"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "街金の社長っつってもウチは秘書がしっかりしてるから"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "少しくらい俺がフラフラしてても大丈夫なんだ\r\n気にしないで"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "遥ちゃんは？　桐生さんがよくなったら沖縄のあの養護施設に\r\nアサガオに戻ることになるのかな？"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "たぶんそうなると思います"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "私やおじさんにはあのアサガオが家で\r\nあそこに住んでいる子供たちが“家族”ですから"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "そっか\r\nじゃあ神室町もまた寂しくなるな"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "なんやサツの旦那方　えらい怖い顔して\r\n患者ら怖がっとんで"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "俺に用やろ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "あ？"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "脱獄で捕まんのはこれで２回目やな"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "話が早くて助かるな　酌量の余地はある\r\n冴島大河　おとなしくしろよ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "じたばたする気なんかあらへん"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "チッくそが\r\nなんで兄弟ばっかりこんな目に遭うんや！"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "ええんや\r\nあとのことは頼んだで兄弟"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "お前らが東城会でごたごたの後始末しとる間\r\n俺はムショでラクさせてもらう"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "それから　"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "桐生一馬の病室はそこだな"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "あ？　なんやと？"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "警視庁の者です\r\nどうかそのままで"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "え？"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||a01_050||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "桐生一馬を　神室町での暴行傷害\r\nならびに器物破損の容疑で逮捕します"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Haruka."
msgstr "Haruka."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "It's good to see you."
msgstr "Che bello vederti."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "How are things?"
msgstr "Come vanno le cose?"

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Things haven't changed much, actually."
msgstr "Le cose non sono cambiate molto, in realtà."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Morning Glory's just like you left it.\r\nEveryone's doing really well."
msgstr "Il Morning Glory è proprio come l'hai lasciato.\r\nStanno tutti molto bene."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "That's great."
msgstr "È fantastico."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I'm glad to hear it."
msgstr "Sono contento di sentirlo."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "The others really wanted to see you too,\r\nbut it would've cost a fortune to get them all here."
msgstr "Anche gli altri volevano davvero vederti,\r\nma sarebbe costato una fortuna portarli tutti qui."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Everyone down in Okinawa is treating us\r\nwell though. You don't need to worry about us."
msgstr "Comunque tutti ad Okinawa ci stanno trattando\r\nbene. Non devi preoccuparti per noi."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "And the media?"
msgstr "E i media?"

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "There have been a few reporters, but..."
msgstr "Ci sono stati un paio di giornalisti, ma..."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "...I've handled them."
msgstr "...li ho gestiti."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry, Haruka."
msgstr "Mi dispiace, Haruka."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "There's not much I can do for you now."
msgstr "Non c'è molto che io possa fare per te ora."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "I should be out in three years\r\nif I can make parole, though."
msgstr "Dovrei uscire tra tre anni\r\nse ottengo la libertà vigilata, però."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "I should be out in three years\r\nif I can make parole, though."
msgstr "Dovrei uscire tra tre anni\r\nse ottengo la libertà vigilata, però."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Three years... That's a long time."
msgstr "Tre anni... È molto tempo."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I..."
msgstr "Io..."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "I'm going to make sure you're never\r\nashamed to call me family again."
msgstr "Farò in modo che tu non ti debba\r\npiù vergognare di chiamarmi famiglia."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "That's what these three years are for."
msgstr "A questo servono questi tre anni."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "What's wrong?"
msgstr "Cosa c'è che non va?"

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Well..."
msgstr "Beh..."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Once I became an idol, it really hurt\r\nhaving to keep my distance from you."
msgstr "Quando sono diventata una idol, ha fatto davvero male\r\ndover mantenere le distanze da te."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "Hm?"

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I'm not saying I regret my decision."
msgstr "Non sto dicendo che rimpiango la mia decisione."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "It's actually the opposite."
msgstr "In realtà è il contrario."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "All that time apart helped me realize\r\nhow close we really are, Uncle Kaz."
msgstr "Tutto quel tempo separati mi ha aiutato a capire\r\nquanto siamo davvero vicini, zio Kaz."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "So when I told the world how I felt\r\nabout you up on that stage..."
msgstr "Quindi quando ho detto al mondo cosa provavo\r\nper te su quel palco..."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "...I meant it."
msgstr "...Ero seria."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Until then, I had always taken\r\nour time together for granted."
msgstr "Fino ad allora, avevo sempre dato\r\nil nostro tempo insieme per scontato."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "I mean, I was just a kid."
msgstr "Insomma, ero solo una bambina."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "That stuff had never really\r\ncrossed my mind before."
msgstr "Quella roba non mi era mai davvero\r\npassata per la testa prima d'ora."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "But that's why even if we're not\r\ntogether... I'll keep my chin up."
msgstr "Ma ecco perché anche se non siamo\r\ninsieme... Terrò la testa alta."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "No matter how far apart we are,\r\nwe're still family. I know that in my heart."
msgstr "Non importa quanto siamo lontani,\r\nsiamo ancora una famiglia. Lo so nel mio cuore."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "That's what I came to tell you today."
msgstr "Questo è quello che sono venuta a dirti oggi."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "It would be too embarrassing to say\r\nit once we're living together again..."
msgstr "Sarebbe troppo imbarazzante dirlo\r\nuna volta che vivremo di nuovo insieme..."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "I get that."
msgstr "Lo capisco."

msgctxt "7||a01_060||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "I should be out in three years\r\nif I can make parole, though."
msgstr "Dovrei uscire tra tre anni\r\nse ottengo la libertà vigilata, però."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hey, dinner's ready."
msgstr "Ehi, la cena è pronta."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Get all this stuff off the table!"
msgstr "Togliete tutta questa roba dal tavolo!"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Koji, you can't just leave your\r\nmanga lying around like this."
msgstr "Koji, non puoi semplicemente lasciare i tuoi\r\nmanga in giro in questo modo."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Izumi, can you get some\r\nwater for everyone?"
msgstr "Izumi, puoi prendere un po' di\r\nacqua per tutti?"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr "Okay!"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Hey Shiro, tablet away when\r\nyou're at the dinner table."
msgstr "Ehi Shiro, via il tablet quando\r\nsei a tavola per cenare."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Just give me a second.\r\nI'm almost finished checking my stocks."
msgstr "Dammi solo un secondo.\r\nHo quasi finito di controllare le mie azioni."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "You're not really playing\r\nthe market on that thing, are you?"
msgstr "Non stai davvero giocando\r\nin borsa su quel coso, vero?"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Like we have the cash for that.\r\nIt's just a simulation."
msgstr "Come se avessimo i soldi per farlo.\r\nÈ solo una simulazione."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Mitsuo still isn't home from practice."
msgstr "Mitsuo non è ancora tornato dall'allenamento."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "He's going all out, huh?"
msgstr "Ci sta dando dentro, eh?"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Baseball's his life.\r\nWonder if he'll get that scholarship."
msgstr "Il baseball è la sua vita.\r\nMi chiedo se otterrà quella borsa di studio."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I'm back."
msgstr "Sono tornato."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "We're home!"
msgstr "Siamo a casa!"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Haruka-chan, we have enough for seconds?"
msgstr "Haruka-chan, ce n'è abbastanza per fare il bis?"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "There's more rice, yeah."
msgstr "C'è altro riso, sì."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I'm good for today."
msgstr "Per oggi sono a posto."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I promised Oshiro I'd train with\r\nhim some more after dinner."
msgstr "Ho promesso a Oshiro che mi sarei allenato ancora un po' con\r\nlui dopo cena."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz is gonna be so surprised\r\nwhen he gets out of jail."
msgstr "Lo zio Kaz sarà così sorpreso\r\nquando uscirà di prigione."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Who'd have guessed Mitsuo would\r\nend up a pro baseball player?"
msgstr "Chi avrebbe mai immaginato che Mitsuo\r\nsarebbe diventato un giocatore di baseball professionista?"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Don't jinx him, you dummy.\r\nHe's still just in middle school."
msgstr "Non portargli sfiga, stupido.\r\nÈ ancora alle scuole medie."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "But if he's competing for\r\na scholarship..."
msgstr "Ma se sta competendo per\r\nuna borsa di studio..."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Mitsuo must have worked really hard."
msgstr "Mitsuo deve aver lavorato davvero sodo."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Koji was the one showing him the ropes,\r\nbut now he's just getting shown up."
msgstr "Era Koji che gli insegnava le basi,\r\nma ora lo sta proprio surclassando."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Shut up!"
msgstr "Zitto!"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Nothing's decided yet though.\r\nThere are other candidates too."
msgstr "Niente è ancora deciso, però.\r\nCi sono anche altri candidati."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Apparently they look into all sorts of stuff.\r\nYour grades, your living situation..."
msgstr "A quanto pare indagano su un sacco di cose.\r\nI tuoi voti, la tua situazione familiare..."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Wait, living situation...?"
msgstr "Aspetta, situazione familiare...?"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Ain't it bad if you're here then?"
msgstr "Non è un male se tu sei qui allora?"

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Dumbass."
msgstr "Deficiente."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "But seriously..."
msgstr "Ma sul serio..."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "It'll be fine. Everyone knows I'm one\r\nof the kids from Morning Glory."
msgstr "Andrà bene. Tutti sanno che sono uno\r\ndei bambini del Morning Glory."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "And they approached me anyway."
msgstr "E mi hanno contattato lo stesso."

msgctxt "8||a01_070||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "If the scholarship doesn't work out,\r\nit just means I wasn't good enough."
msgstr "Se la borsa di studio non dovesse andare in porto,\r\nvoldrà dire semplicemente che non ero abbastanza bravo."

msgctxt "9||a01_075||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "No..."
msgstr "No..."

msgctxt "9||a01_075||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz... I..."
msgstr "Zio Kaz... Io..."

msgctxt "9||a01_075||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "What am I supposed to do?"
msgstr "Cosa dovrei fare?"

msgctxt "9||a01_075||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I knew it."
msgstr "Lo sapevo."

msgctxt "9||a01_075||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "(Yakuza girl Haruka spotted at Morning Glory)"
msgstr "(La ragazza della yakuza, Haruka, avvistata al Morning Glory)"

msgctxt "9||a01_075||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "(It's scary how Haruka Sawamura\r\njust waltzed back to Okinawa.)"
msgstr "(È spaventoso come Haruka Sawamura\r\nsia semplicemente tornata a Okinawa come se niente fosse.)"

msgctxt "9||a01_075||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "(Morning Glory's a yakuza safe house!)"
msgstr "(Il Morning Glory è un rifugio sicuro per la yakuza!)"

msgctxt "9||a01_075||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "I never should have come back here..."
msgstr "Non sarei mai dovuta tornare qui..."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "I'm so sorry, everyone."
msgstr "Mi dispiace tanto, ragazzi."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Ayako."
msgstr "Ayako."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "So you're really leaving, Haruka-chan."
msgstr "Quindi te ne stai davvero andando, Haruka-chan."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "It's because of this, isn't it?"
msgstr "È a causa di questo, vero?"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "It's because of this, isn't it?"
msgstr "È a causa di questo, vero?"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "Oh."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "So you saw it too, Ayako."
msgstr "Quindi l'hai visto anche tu, Ayako."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Are you worried about\r\nMitsuo's scholarship?"
msgstr "Sei preoccupata per la borsa\r\ndi studio di Mitsuo?"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "It's not just about him."
msgstr "Non si tratta solo di lui."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Any one of you could end up with\r\nbig chances like that in the future."
msgstr "Ognuno di voi potrebbe trovarsi con\r\ngrandi opportunità del genere in futuro."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "If you lost them because of me..."
msgstr "Se le perdeste a causa mia..."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "...I'd never forgive myself."
msgstr "...non me lo perdonerei mai."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I never realized how harsh life can be."
msgstr "Non mi sono mai resa conto di quanto possa essere dura la vita."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz did, though."
msgstr "Lo zio Kaz sì, però."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "That's why he's in jail now."
msgstr "Ecco perché ora è in prigione."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "So what?"
msgstr "E allora?"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "What are you gonna do once you leave?\r\nWhere are you gonna go?"
msgstr "Cosa farai una volta andata via?\r\nDove andrai?"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I want to be closer to Uncle Kaz."
msgstr "Voglio stare più vicina allo zio Kaz."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "What do you mean? You know it's gonna\r\nbe years until he gets out, right?"
msgstr "Cosa intendi? Sai che ci vorranno\r\nanni prima che esca, vero?"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "(Exclusive! Where is the Yakuza Idol\r\nHaruka Sawamura Six Months Later!?)"
msgstr "(Esclusiva! Dov'è finita l'Idol della Yakuza\r\nHaruka Sawamura sei mesi dopo!?)"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "(Ex-Tojo Clan Yakuza, K-san, Has Deep\r\nTies to Okinawan Orphanage)"
msgstr "(Un ex-membro della Yakuza del Clan Tojo, K-san, ha profondi\r\nlegami con un orfanotrofio di Okinawa)"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Does he know you're leaving Morning Glory?"
msgstr "Lui sa che stai lasciando il Morning Glory?"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "No. I came to this decision all on my own."
msgstr "No. Ho preso questa decisione da sola."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "I'll write him a letter to say\r\nyou're coming, then."
msgstr "Allora gli scriverò una lettera per dirgli\r\nche stai arrivando."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Don't."
msgstr "Non farlo."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Eh?"

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "I'll explain everything to him\r\nonce we're together."
msgstr "Gli spiegherò tutto\r\nuna volta che saremo insieme."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr "Addio."

msgctxt "10||a01_076||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "It's because of this, isn't it?"
msgstr "È a causa di questo, vero?"

msgctxt "11||a01_077||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Does he know you're leaving Morning Glory?"
msgstr "Lui sa che stai lasciando il Morning Glory?"

msgctxt "11||a01_077||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "No. I came to this decision all on my own."
msgstr "No. Ho preso questa decisione da sola."

msgctxt "11||a01_077||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I'll write him a letter to say\r\nyou're coming, then."
msgstr "Allora gli scriverò una lettera per dirgli\r\nche stai arrivando."

msgctxt "11||a01_077||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Don't."
msgstr "Non farlo."

msgctxt "11||a01_077||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Eh?"

msgctxt "11||a01_077||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I'll explain everything to him\r\nonce we're together."
msgstr "Gli spiegherò tutto\r\nuna volta che saremo insieme."

msgctxt "11||a01_077||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr "Addio."

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Several fires were reported all around\r\nLittle Asia at roughly the same time."
msgstr "Sono stati segnalati diversi incendi in giro\r\nper Little Asia quasi contemporaneamente."

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Do you think it's arson?"
msgstr "Pensi che sia doloso?"

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Fire department better be on the way.\r\nHow's the evac going?"
msgstr "I vigili del fuoco faranno meglio a essere per strada.\r\nCome procede l'evacuazione?"

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Well, sir!\r\nIt's spreading quickly though..."
msgstr "Bene, signore!\r\nSi sta diffondendo rapidamente, però..."

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "What a mess..."
msgstr "Che disastro..."

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Little Asia's gonna burn to cinders."
msgstr "Little Asia diventerà cenere."

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "What do you think?\r\nQuite a view, isn't it?"
msgstr "Che ne dite?\r\nUn bel panorama, vero?"

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "These flames should serve as\r\nproof of our dedication to the cause."
msgstr "Queste fiamme dovrebbero servire come\r\nprova della nostra dedizione alla causa."

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Gentlemen, lasting prosperity is\r\nnow within arm's reach."
msgstr "Signori, una prosperità duratura è\r\nora a portata di mano."

msgctxt "14||a01_080||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Shall we toast to that?"
msgstr "Vogliamo brindare a questo?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "U-Uncle Kaz?"
msgstr "Z-Zio Kaz?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Izumi?"
msgstr "Izumi?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "You're taller than I remember."
msgstr "Sei più alta di quanto ricordassi."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz! Wait, you're really here!?\r\nHow'd you get back so soon!?"
msgstr "Zio Kaz! Aspetta, sei davvero qui!?\r\nCome hai fatto a tornare così presto!?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Did I surprise you?"
msgstr "Ti ho sorpresa?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Hey, Uncle Kaz is back!\r\nHe's back, everyone!"
msgstr "Ehi, lo zio Kaz è tornato!\r\nÈ tornato, ragazzi!"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr "Zio Kaz!"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Taichi!"
msgstr "Taichi!"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "You jerk! I thought you were\r\nnever gonna come home."
msgstr "Brutto stupido! Pensavo che non saresti\r\nmai più tornato a casa."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Why'd you make us wait so long!?"
msgstr "Perché ci hai fatto aspettare così tanto!?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry, Taichi."
msgstr "Mi dispiace, Taichi."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "You guys have gotten really big."
msgstr "Ragazzi, siete diventati davvero grandi."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "How many years has it been?"
msgstr "Quanti anni sono passati?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "All of you look so grown up."
msgstr "Sembrate tutti così cresciuti."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Hey, where's Haruka-chan?\r\nYou came together, right?"
msgstr "Ehi, dov'è Haruka-chan?\r\nSiete venuti insieme, vero?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah!\r\nShe'll be here soon, right?"
msgstr "Oh già!\r\nSarà qui a breve, no?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "No, she's not with me."
msgstr "No, non è con me."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Is Haruka not around?"
msgstr "Haruka non c'è?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "What do you mean, Uncle Kaz?\r\nShe said she'd be with you."
msgstr "Cosa intendi, zio Kaz?\r\nHa detto che sarebbe stata con te."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "Mh?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Yeah, that's what she said."
msgstr "Già, è quello che ha detto."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Ain't that right, Ayako-chan?"
msgstr "Non è vero, Ayako-chan?"

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry."
msgstr "Mi dispiace."

msgctxt "15||a01_090||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "I'm so sorry!"
msgstr "Mi dispiace tanto!"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Haruka-chan left Morning Glory just\r\nabout three years ago now."
msgstr "Haruka-chan ha lasciato il Morning Glory\r\ncirca tre anni fa."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "We got calls from her at first,\r\nbut those stopped in the past year or so."
msgstr "All'inizio ricevevamo le sue chiamate,\r\nma da circa un anno a questa parte si sono interrotte."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "It all felt so strange. She's not\r\nthe kind of person to just disappear."
msgstr "Era tutto così strano. Non è il\r\ntipo di persona che scompare nel nulla."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "She said she was living near you, though."
msgstr "Ha detto che stava vivendo vicino a te, però."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Why don't we just call her already!?\r\nCome on!"
msgstr "Perché non la chiamiamo, e basta!?\r\nSu, dai!"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "We don't have any way to reach her.\r\nAll her calls have been from pay phones."
msgstr "Non abbiamo alcun modo per rintracciarla.\r\nTutte le sue chiamate provenivano da telefoni pubblici."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "She apparently canceled her cell contract\r\nright after she left Morning Glory."
msgstr "A quanto pare ha annullato il suo contratto telefonico\r\nsubito dopo aver lasciato il Morning Glory."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Why didn't she tell us any of this herself?"
msgstr "Perché non ci ha detto niente di tutto questo lei stessa?"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "You and her always treat us like\r\nwe're just a bunch of little kids!"
msgstr "Tu e lei ci trattate sempre come\r\nse fossimo solo un branco di bambini piccoli!"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry. I just..."
msgstr "Mi dispiace. Io solo..."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "I didn't want you to worry."
msgstr "Non volevo che vi preoccupaste."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Besides, I really thought there was\r\na chance she'd come back with Uncle Kaz."
msgstr "Inoltre, pensavo davvero che ci fosse la\r\npossibilità che tornasse con lo zio Kaz."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "But still! Why'd Haruka-chan have to\r\nleave us here in the first place?"
msgstr "Eppure! Perché Haruka-chan ha dovuto\r\nlasciarci qui, per cominciare?"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Things were good, weren't they?"
msgstr "Le cose andavano bene, no?"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Does Haruka-chan...\r\nnot like us anymore?"
msgstr "Haruka-chan...\r\nnon ci vuole più bene?"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "That's not it. She doesn't want to\r\nhold us back. That's what she told me."
msgstr "Non è questo. Non vuole essere\r\nun peso. È questo che mi ha detto."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Huh? Hold us back?\r\nWhat's that supposed to mean?"
msgstr "Eh? Essere un peso per noi?\r\nChe diavolo dovrebbe significare?"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Right around when Mitsuo was up for that\r\nbaseball scholarship from his school..."
msgstr "Proprio quando Mitsuo era in lizza per quella\r\nborsa di studio per il baseball dalla sua scuola..."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "...this article got published."
msgstr "...questo articolo è stato pubblicato."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "I think Haruka-chan hated the idea of\r\nher actions turning people against us."
msgstr "Penso che Haruka-chan odiasse l'idea che le\r\nsue azioni potessero mettere le persone contro di noi."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Plus, back then, we didn't know how\r\nMitsuo's career would play out yet."
msgstr "Inoltre, all'epoca, non sapevamo ancora\r\ncome si sarebbe evoluta la carriera di Mitsuo."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "What? Are you trying to pin this on me!?"
msgstr "Cosa? Stai cercando di dare la colpa a me!?"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "No, that's not what she meant."
msgstr "No, non è quello che intendeva."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "It's not your fault, Mitsuo.\r\nAnd it's not Haruka's either."
msgstr "Non è colpa tua, Mitsuo.\r\nE non è nemmeno di Haruka."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "The blame... is all on me."
msgstr "La colpa... è tutta mia."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz..."
msgstr "Zio Kaz..."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "I'm going to find Haruka.\r\nI swear."
msgstr "Troverò Haruka.\r\nLo giuro."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "I'll bring her back."
msgstr "La riporterò a casa."

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "(Exclusive! Where is the Yakuza Idol\r\nHaruka Sawamura Six Months Later!?)"
msgstr "(Esclusiva! Dov'è finita l'Idol della Yakuza\r\nHaruka Sawamura sei mesi dopo!?)"

msgctxt "16||a01_100||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "(Ex-Tojo Clan Yakuza, K-san, Has Deep\r\nTies to Okinawan Orphanage)"
msgstr "(Un ex-membro della Yakuza del Clan Tojo, K-san, ha profondi\r\nlegami con un orfanotrofio di Okinawa)"

msgctxt "17||a01_110||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "How do I always end up\r\nback in this damn city?"
msgstr "Come faccio a finire sempre\r\nin questa maledetta città?"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "I appreciate the courage\r\nyou've shown in coming here."
msgstr "Apprezzo il coraggio\r\nche avete dimostrato venendo qui."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "However, there will be no tolerance\r\nfor Tojo arrogance here in Little Asia."
msgstr "Tuttavia, non ci sarà alcuna tolleranza per\r\nl'arroganza del Tojo qui a Little Asia."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Ed-san."
msgstr "Ed-san."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "You'll have to take this at face value,\r\nbut we aren't looking for violence today."
msgstr "Dovrai prenderla per buona, ma oggi\r\nnon siamo in cerca di violenza."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "All we want is for your boss to\r\nhear what we have to say."
msgstr "Tutto ciò che vogliamo è che il tuo boss\r\nascolti ciò che abbiamo da dirgli."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "We risked our lives to even get here."
msgstr "Abbiamo rischiato la vita anche solo per arrivare qui."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "If you're really here to talk, what are you\r\ndoing with that gun in your pocket?"
msgstr "Se siete davvero qui per parlare, che ci\r\nfate con quella pistola in tasca?"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "You'd have us stroll into triad turf\r\nwithout some form of self-defense?"
msgstr "Vorresti che passeggiassimo nel territorio della Triade\r\nsenza alcun tipo di difesa personale?"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Let's just keep this civil."
msgstr "Cerchiamo di mantenere un tono civile."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "There is little need for conversation\r\nwhen it's clear what the Tojo Clan wants."
msgstr "C'è poco bisogno di conversare quando\r\nè chiaro cosa vuole il Clan Tojo."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "You'd like us to confine ourselves to\r\nthis tiny box that is Little Asia, yes?"
msgstr "Vorreste che ci confinassimo in questa\r\npiccola scatola che è Little Asia, vero?"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Exactly."
msgstr "Esattamente."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "In exchange, we're prepared to officially\r\nrecognize Little Asia as your territory."
msgstr "In cambio, siamo pronti a riconoscere\r\nufficialmente Little Asia come vostro territorio."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Just make sure your boss understands..."
msgstr "Assicurati solo che il tuo boss capisca..."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "If any triads take so much as a step\r\noutside of Little Asia's borders..."
msgstr "Se un qualsiasi membro della triade dovesse fare anche solo\r\nun passo al di fuori dei confini di Little Asia..."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "...We will show them no mercy."
msgstr "...non avremo pietà."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "So, what? Are you saying you've\r\nbeen lenient prior to today?"
msgstr "E allora? State dicendo che siete stati\r\nclementi prima di oggi?"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Yes, very perceptive."
msgstr "Sì, molto perspicace."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "My boss has already given me\r\nhis answer to your ultimatum."
msgstr "Il mio boss mi ha già dato la\r\nsua risposta al vostro ultimatum."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Though I'm worried you won't understand.\r\nMy Japanese isn't so great, after all."
msgstr "Anche se temo che non capirete.\r\nIl mio giapponese non è un granché, dopotutto."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Nonsense."
msgstr "Sciocchezze."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "You speak better than most of\r\nthe younger members of our clan."
msgstr "Parli meglio della maggior parte\r\ndei membri più giovani del nostro clan."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Do I really?"
msgstr "Davvero?"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Even so, I'd rather you convey our\r\nmessage to your boss in your own words."
msgstr "Anche se fosse così, preferirei che comunicassi il nostro\r\nmessaggio al tuo capo con parole tue."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "He'll want to know everything\r\nthat's about to happen."
msgstr "Vorrà sapere tutto quello\r\nche sta per succedere."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Eh?"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Hey, what do you think you're doing!?"
msgstr "Ehi, cosa credi di fare!?"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "If you were going to shoot,\r\nyou should've done it."
msgstr "Se avevi intenzione di sparare,\r\navresti dovuto farlo."

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Shit!"
msgstr "Merda!"

msgctxt "18||a01_120||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "This is the Saio Triad's answer."
msgstr "Questa è la risposta della Triade Saio."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "...Akiyama?"
msgstr "...Akiyama?"

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "Hm?"

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Wait, what the?\r\nKiryu-san!?"
msgstr "Aspetta, che cavolo...?\r\nKiryu-san!?"

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "It's been a while."
msgstr "È passato un po' di tempo."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Er... Well..."
msgstr "Ehm... Beh..."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Come on in.\r\nTake a load off."
msgstr "Vieni dentro.\r\nRiposati."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "As you can probably tell,\r\nthat's about all I can offer."
msgstr "Come puoi ben immaginare,\r\nquesto è praticamente tutto ciò che posso offrire."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I've been looking for you."
msgstr "Ti stavo cercando."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Rumor has it you closed down Sky Finance."
msgstr "Gira voce che hai chiuso la Sky Finance."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Yeah, well..."
msgstr "Già, beh..."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Couldn't tell you why, but the triads\r\nkinda want my head on a stick."
msgstr "Non saprei dirti perché, ma le triadi\r\nvogliono la mia testa su una picca."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Figured I'd take a little break."
msgstr "Ho pensato di prendermi una piccola pausa."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Not like I'll stay down here forever, though."
msgstr "Non è che resterò qui sotto per sempre, però."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I've heard all about that."
msgstr "Ho sentito tutto a riguardo."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Sounds like Kamurocho's having\r\nsome rough times these days."
msgstr "Sembra che Kamurocho stia attraversando\r\nmomenti difficili in questi giorni."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I even had to send my secretary\r\nback to her family in the countryside."
msgstr "Già. Ho persino dovuto mandare la mia segretaria\r\ndi nuovo dalla sua famiglia in campagna."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "It got too dangerous to risk keeping her\r\nin the middle of this mess."
msgstr "Era diventato troppo pericoloso rischiare di tenerla\r\nnel bel mezzo di questo casino."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Makes sense."
msgstr "Ha senso."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "That said, you're looking better\r\nthan I was expecting."
msgstr "Detto questo, hai un aspetto migliore\r\ndi quanto mi aspettassi."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Same to you, Kiryu-san. Glad to see\r\nyou're finally back on the street."
msgstr "Altrettanto, Kiryu-san. Sono felice di vedere\r\nche sei finalmente tornato per strada."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "But, what are you doing in Kamurocho?"
msgstr "Ma cosa ci fai a Kamurocho?"

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I came to see you."
msgstr "Sono venuto per vederti."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "As for why..."
msgstr "Il motivo per cui l'ho fatto..."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "...I thought you might have some\r\nidea of where Haruka is."
msgstr "...è perché ho pensato che potessi avere una\r\nqualche idea di dove si trovi Haruka."

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Haruka-chan?"
msgstr "Haruka-chan?"

msgctxt "19||a01_130||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "You mean she didn't go back to Morning Glory?"
msgstr "Vuoi dire che non è tornata al Morning Glory?"

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Ah! Man, it feels good to get some sun."
msgstr "Ah! Cavolo, fa bene prendere un po' di sole."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "The air's so fresh, too."
msgstr "E l'aria è così fresca."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Sorry about that, Akiyama."
msgstr "Mi dispiace per questo, Akiyama."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I led them right to you."
msgstr "Li ho portati dritto da te."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Don't worry about it. I was getting\r\nbored of sleeping the days away."
msgstr "Non preoccuparti. Mi stavo annoiando\r\na dormire tutto il giorno."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Anyway, let's not stick around.\r\nWouldn't want Ed to show up with an army."
msgstr "Comunque, non restiamo nei paraggi.\r\nNon vorrei che Ed si presentasse con un esercito."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "It's Date-san."
msgstr "È Date-san."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Kiryu. Where are you?"
msgstr "Kiryu. Dove sei?"

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "In Kamurocho. I'm over at\r\nthe Children's Park with Akiyama."
msgstr "A Kamurocho. Sono al\r\nChildren's Park con Akiyama."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Got it. Think the two of you\r\ncould come by Touto Hospital?"
msgstr "Ricevuto. Pensi che voi due\r\npossiate passare dal Touto Hospital?"

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "Mh?"

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "I have some bad news. I'm not\r\nsure of all the details yet..."
msgstr "Ho delle brutte notizie. Non sono\r\nancora sicuro di tutti i dettagli..."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "But it's Haruka."
msgstr "Ma riguarda Haruka."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "She's been in an accident in Kamurocho."
msgstr "Ha avuto un incidente a Kamurocho."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "They're not sure if she'll pull through."
msgstr "Non sono sicuri se ce la farà."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Hold on a second!"
msgstr "Aspetta un attimo!"

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Haruka was in Kamurocho?"
msgstr "Haruka era a Kamurocho?"

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "Cosa?"

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "I'll fill you in once you're here.\r\nHurry."
msgstr "Ti aggiornerò una volta che sarai qui.\r\nSbrigati."

msgctxt "20||a01_140||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Hey, hold on! Kiryu-san!"
msgstr "Ehi, aspetta! Kiryu-san!"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Kiryu!"
msgstr "Kiryu!"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Date-san!"
msgstr "Date-san!"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Excuse me, are you a patient here?"
msgstr "Mi scusi, è un paziente qui?"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Well, uh..."
msgstr "Beh, uh..."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "If not, I must ask you to leave.\r\nYour hygiene is a health hazard!"
msgstr "Se non lo è, devo chiederle di andarsene.\r\nLa sua igiene è un pericolo per la salute!"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "This is one of my coworkers on the force."
msgstr "Questo è uno dei miei colleghi in polizia."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "He's the one who let me know\r\nabout Haruka's accident."
msgstr "È stato lui a farmi sapere\r\ndell'incidente di Haruka."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "The name's Honjo. Date-san's told\r\nme a great deal about you."
msgstr "Il mio nome è Honjo. Date-san mi\r\nha parlato molto di te."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What about Haruka?\r\nWhere is she!?"
msgstr "E Haruka?\r\nDov'è!?"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "In the ICU. She's in no state\r\nto be accepting visitors."
msgstr "In terapia intensiva. Non è in condizioni\r\ndi ricevere visite."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "She fractured both her hip and shoulder,\r\nbut the cranial damage is life threatening."
msgstr "Si è fratturata l'anca e la spalla,\r\nma i danni cranici sono pericolosi per la vita."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "She's in critical condition,\r\nunconscious at the moment."
msgstr "È in condizioni critiche,\r\nal momento è priva di sensi."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Wh-What happened?"
msgstr "C-cosa è successo?"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "It was a hit-and-run."
msgstr "È stato un pirata della strada."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Some reckless punk drove into her.\r\nThe culprit's still at large."
msgstr "Qualche teppista incosciente l'ha investita.\r\nIl colpevole è ancora a piede libero."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "A hit-and-run..."
msgstr "Un pirata della strada..."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Are you okay, Kiryu?"
msgstr "Stai bene, Kiryu?"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "No. I can barely think straight."
msgstr "No. Riesco a malapena a pensare lucidamente."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "I can imagine."
msgstr "Posso immaginare."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "But there's another piece to the puzzle."
msgstr "Ma c'è un altro pezzo del puzzle."

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "Che vuoi dire?"

msgctxt "21||a01_150||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Come with me.\r\nI need to show you something."
msgstr "Vieni con me.\r\nDevo mostrarti qualcosa."

msgctxt "22||a01_160||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Just over there."
msgstr "Proprio laggiù."

msgctxt "22||a01_160||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "Hm?"

msgctxt "22||a01_160||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Haruka was clutching someone tight\r\nwhen she saw the car coming."
msgstr "Haruka stava stringendo forte qualcuno\r\nquando ha visto la macchina arrivare."

msgctxt "22||a01_160||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "A life she wanted to protect,\r\neven if it meant risking her own."
msgstr "Una vita che voleva proteggere,\r\nanche se significava rischiare la propria."

msgctxt "22||a01_160||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "Cosa!?"

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "This child..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "...is Haruka's?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I don't believe it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Well, it's time to start.\r\nLook at his name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "It's Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "There's no doubt, he's Haruka's kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "No way...\r\nYou're sure!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "The last name's just icing on the cake."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Haruka would've died to keep him safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "That's only a mother's sacrifice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||a02_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "<font_kind=yakuza_italic>Haruto Sawamura</font_kind>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "It's an honor to have you here,\r\nFourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Good afternoon. I'm Someya,\r\nPatriarch of the Someya Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Your recent stint in jail was very\r\nmuch appreciated. You did well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "So you knew I'd come back?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "You'll have to forgive the actions of\r\nmy subordinate, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "He's caused a misunderstanding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "And what exactly do you mean by that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Let's table that conversation for now.\r\nPerhaps we can discuss further inside?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I'm sure your time behind bars has\r\nleft you exhausted, and besides..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Sugai-san has been looking forward\r\nto meeting you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "You know of Sugai-san, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "His Tojo history may be longer than\r\nyours, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "With the sixth chairman indisposed for\r\nhis trial, Sugai-san is acting chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "And he's the one who had\r\nthat guy trailing me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Again, let's talk inside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "I would love to be regaled by the tales\r\nof your days as a young yakuza, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I'm sure we could all stand to learn a thing\r\nor two from a man as accomplished as you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||a02_020||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Excuse me.\r\nApologies for the intrusion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Come in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I've brought the fourth chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Long time no see, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Do you remember me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "It appears the answer is no..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Well, I've only ever been an advisor,\r\neven under the sixth chairman's rule."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I don't blame you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "As I'm sure you heard, they called on me\r\nto step in after the sixth chairman's arrest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Just as the Tojo Clan was getting younger,\r\nthe old guard swoops in to fix things."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "We must seem rather unstable in your eyes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "This is quite a table you brought in here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Yakuza seem to talk more with\r\nour pens than our fists these days."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Another sign of the times."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "And Someya over there? He doesn't\r\nlook like much of a paper pusher to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "I leave the math to the number crunchers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Every yakuza has his role to play, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Please. Take a seat, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "I don't plan on staying long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "But before I go,\r\nI do have a few questions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I assume this is about the hit-and-run\r\non your sweet Haruka?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "What a terrible tragedy.\r\nYou have my condolences."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "When did you hear about Haruka's\r\naccident? Who told you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I was informed by the police\r\nnot long after the incident."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Do they tell you everything\r\nthat happens in Kamurocho?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "It's no secret that Haruka Sawamura is\r\nvery special to you, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Naturally, that significance is what led\r\nthe police to contact us so quickly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Did you have any other questions for me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "At the scene of the accident,\r\nthere was a man spying on me with a camera."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "He said he was with the Someya Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Did you give that order, Sugai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "It wasn't spying.\r\nIt was protection."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "We've been looking for you ever since\r\nwe heard you'd returned to Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Checking in on you at the scene of the accident\r\nwas the only way to confirm your well-being."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "Someya speaks the truth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "I honestly thought it a bit extreme."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "But we're at war with the Chinese, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Though you're a civilian now, they may not\r\nhave extended you a civilian's courtesy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "I didn't ask for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "And I don't need your help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "You're a man of strong character,\r\nFourth Chairman. I'm well aware of that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "Hence why I chose to act in secret.\r\nYou would never knowingly accept our help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "My apologies if I've upset you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "Didn't I tell you, Sugai-san? The fourth\r\nchairman doesn't need our protection."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "It'd be pointless for the Chinese\r\nto target him anyway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "The Dragon of Dojima is dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "Any weight that name carried is gone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "We may have been watching you, yes...\r\nBut don't assume you have any value to us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "The current conflict rests on\r\nmy generation, not yours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "It has nothing to do with a fossil like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "The new generation sounds pretty cocky.\r\n"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "This war with the Chinese\r\nhas left us no choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "And is it any wonder?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "Until recently, the yakuza's power\r\nwas vested in its financial prowess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "So it follows that the sixth chairman's\r\nofficers were all very intelligent men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "But, now things have changed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||59||||4"
msgid "With the Tojo Clan at war, all that matters\r\nnow is whether or not a yakuza can fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||60||||4"
msgid "Your value as a yakuza has a direct\r\ncorrelation to your body count."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||61||||4"
msgid "In other words, you ascend by force.\r\nIt's the dawn of a new era for us yakuza."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||62||||4"
msgid "Doesn't that sound amazing,\r\nFourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||63||||4"
msgid "You rose to power in much the same way,\r\ndidn't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||64||||4"
msgid "Now even the once invincible Sugai-san\r\nhas to rely on youth to keep the clan intact."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||65||||4"
msgid "Isn't that right, Sugai-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "They risk their lives for our cause,\r\nso we promote them. It's only fair."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "I didn't come here today to talk\r\nabout the value of a yakuza."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||68||||4"
msgid "I'm only going to ask this once."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||69||||4"
msgid "Were you involved in Haruka's accident?\r\nYou really know nothing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||70||||4"
msgid "What are you implying? What purpose\r\nwould such a horrible act even serve?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||71||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||72||||4"
msgid "As it stands, I believe you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||73||||4"
msgid "Haruka and I have less than\r\nnothing to do with your little war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||74||||4"
msgid "But hear me now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||75||||4"
msgid "If the Tojo Clan even <font_kind=yakuza_italic>thinks</font_kind>\r\nabout laying a hand on my family..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||76||||4"
msgid "...I will bury all of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||77||||4"
msgid "We aren't interested in making\r\nan enemy of the Dragon of Dojima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||a02_030||cinema_telop||78||||4"
msgid "We have plenty of other playthings\r\nto keep us occupied."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Let's not do this, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "And let Nojiri take him? He doesn't\r\ncare what happens to these kids."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "The only one who can keep this\r\nbaby safe... is me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Maybe, but the guy did have\r\n<font_kind=yakuza_italic>some</font_kind> logic behind him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "People who know you personally are\r\none thing, but to the rest of the world..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "...You're just an ex-con of a yakuza."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry. But there's not much we can do\r\nfor the kid until Haruka-chan wakes up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "We have to let the authorities\r\nhandle this how they see fit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What if Haruka takes a turn for the worse?\r\nHer son would..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "What are you saying, Kiryu-san?\r\nDon't even go down that path!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "How can you know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "They'd put Haruto in an orphanage for sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "And if they did, there'd be nothing I could\r\ndo to help him. We'd be total strangers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I'd never see his face again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "That's what happens when a child\r\ngets sent off to an orphanage like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "No matter how hard I struggle,\r\nit'll be impossible for me to help him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Haruka wouldn't want that\r\nfor her only child."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "You see?\r\nThis is my only chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "What are you doing in here?\r\nGet your hands off that child!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "We're in the middle of something here.\r\nCan you wait outside?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Absolutely not!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Unhand that child this instant!\r\nYou think you can get away with this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "I'm taking him with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I'll give him back once Haruka wakes up.\r\nTrust me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "I can't let you do this, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "You'd get taken back in, this time as\r\na kidnapper. How could I face Haruka?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "You'd really do that to her?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "My choice is made, Akiyama!\r\nYou can't change my mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "I'm trying anyway, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "I'm telling you you're making\r\nthe wrong call here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "For once in your life, think something through!\r\nYou've gotta consider the consequences!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Enough!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "You think I don't know this is wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Whatever happens to me doesn't matter,\r\nand nobody else does either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "I need to protect Haruka's son, now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "I have to do this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "If you're dead-set on stopping me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "...There's only one way forward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Step aside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "Akiyama!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||a02_040||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "Dammit, why won't you listen!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||a02_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Just a little longer, okay?\r\nYou must be starving, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||a02_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "You not <font_kind=yakuza_italic>seriously</font_kind> giving\r\nthat to a baby, are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||a02_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Date-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||a02_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "If it's food you're looking for,\r\ntry something more like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||a02_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "You never change, do you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||a02_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Still a loose cannon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Haruka?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "What happened?\r\nWhat's going on with her?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "She had to have emergency surgery.\r\nThey managed to save her life..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "...But she's still comatose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "The doctors don't know when\r\nshe'll regain consciousness. Or if."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "No way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "How did it come to this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Hey, you went poking your nose\r\naround Kamurocho today, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "You learn anything about what\r\nhappened after Haruka disappeared?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Nothing at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "She left Okinawa, disappeared for\r\nthree years, then showed up here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "That's all I know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "In that case, this is probably\r\nthe only lead we have."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Hm? What's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "A photo we pulled from Haruka's cell data."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "We managed to recover it even though\r\nthe phone got smashed in the accident."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Any idea where it was taken?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "This background tells me nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Well, we actually managed to pull\r\nGPS data from the photo too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "These crazy phones record the\r\nexact spot a picture was taken in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "And that spot is, well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "It's in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Hiroshima?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Yeah, somewhere around Jingaicho,\r\nin the city of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||a02_060||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "You're telling me Haruka left\r\nOkinawa to go to Hiroshima?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Not so bad, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Don't you think, Haruto?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Oh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Is that an accident I smell?\r\nHold on a second."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Hey, no squirming.\r\nI'll be done soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Whoa!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I'm not falling for that one again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Are you hungry?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||a03_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Uh oh...\r\nI'm all out of milk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Haruto.\r\nHere, I got you some milk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Sorry it took so long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "What's wrong?\r\nIsn't this what you wanted!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san?\r\nIt's Kiyomi, from Snack Kiyomi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "O-Oh. It's open!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Come on in!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Ah, figures."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Can I hold him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "This little guy's not hungry at all.\r\nJust sleepy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Sleepy!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Best thing to do now is hold\r\nhim close and wait a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "That's it...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Mhm."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||a03_030||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Seriously?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "You!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Surprised t'see ya still here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Let me guess... Nagumo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Y'don't gotta be so cold."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "We ain't strangers no more. Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I see you brought friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Why are you gunning for me like this?\r\nI don't want any trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Then maybe y'should run on back to Tokyo.\r\nHow 'bout that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Y'know this guy, Cap?\r\nWho is he?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "A mighty fine question!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Y'wanna know who he is?\r\nA filthy outsider from Tokyo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Look at 'im! Don't that ugly mug\r\njus' make ya wanna cry?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Um, Cap..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "We should probably get going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "We're gonna get chewed out again\r\nif we're not there soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Ya turdbrain!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Ow!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Ain't nobody gon' chew us out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Y'hear, Yuta!? Don't go talkin' to\r\nyer captain like that again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "I'm in the middle of somethin' here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "It looks like yer target's\r\nnot interested. See?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "That highfalutin' asshole!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Let's deal with him later, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "We can't start without ya there, Cap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Yer in luck this time, Kiryu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "But listen, y'ain't gon' survive our\r\nnext meetin'! Remember that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "What a mess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||a03_040||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "That guy just won't leave me alone..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I thought Nagumo was supposed\r\nto take baseball seriously."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "He usually does, but today he's\r\nreally out for blood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "C'mon! Y'hurtin'?\r\nDon't y'wanna fight me, Ino!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Let's dance!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "What're y'doin', ya coward!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Y'think yer too cool to throw down, huh!?\r\nHey, I didn't realize yer balls fell off!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Y'know the next batter?\r\nIt's that Kiryu guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Right. Why's Cap been gettin' all\r\nworked up over him anyways?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "He's screwed if he can't focus on the game.\r\nBaseball's his one savin' grace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "It doesn't really matter why. He's just\r\nnot gonna be happy 'til he fights someone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Let's get this over with so we\r\ncan go home in peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Good thinkin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "You sure, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I'm the one Nagumo wants."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "If I'd gone up to bat earlier,\r\nnobody else would've had to get hurt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "So my prey's finally showed up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Y'know, my grip's been\r\nslippin' real bad today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Y'can't blame me fer all\r\nyer guys gettin' hit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Nothin' personal, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I'm gon' smash yer goddamn face in.\r\nWatch close, y'lousy rat!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Dieee!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Looks like my grip's going too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "You can't blame me for\r\nwhere my bat ended up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "That so?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Shall we get going, Matsunaga-aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Yup."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Shit, this ain't good..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "I'm done playin' with ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||a03_050||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "C'mon! It's time fer a whuppin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hey..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Are you sure about this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I mean, don't you think\r\nit's almost time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "No, he should be fine for now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I just want to enjoy my drink\r\nfor a little longer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Outside, now, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Give it a rest already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I don't have any more time\r\nto waste on this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whaddya mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "If you want a fight,\r\nyou'll have to find someone else."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Not everyone's as free as you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||a03_060||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Hey, Nagumo.\r\nJus' the fella I needed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "'Kay, I getcha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "But y'know, that was\r\nonly the first round."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I was... just warmin' up a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "The real whuppin' starts now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I've already spent too long\r\nmessing around with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I said, I ain't through with ya yet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Give it a rest already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I don't have any more time\r\nto waste on this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whaddya mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "If you want to fight, you'll\r\nhave to find someone else."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Not everyone's as free as you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||a03_070||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Hey, Nagumo.\r\nJus' the fella I needed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "I'm done waitin' on yer sorry ass!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Please, I'll pay what I owe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Mama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "It's okay. You shouldn't get involved.\r\nThis isn't your problem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I can't, Kiyo-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I ain't gonna take that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "If I did, well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I wouldn't be able t'look ya\r\nin the eye again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What is this shit, Nagumo!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Y'tryin' to disgrace my family? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Patriarch Masuzoe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "We got our own way of doin' stuff.\r\nDon't take this out on her, I'm beggin' ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Yer that in love with her, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I see. Well if that's what y'wanna do,\r\ny'better be ready fer the consequences!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Apologies fer causin' a scene.\r\nI'll make sure t'buy a drink next time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I'm real sorry 'bout this, Kiyo-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Nagumo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Get yer ass over here! Ain't y'gonna\r\nshow us what bein' a man's about!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "So sorry, Haruto-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "That was scary, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I'll be back.\r\nJust need a little air."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||a03_080||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "I won't be long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "I know I don't deserve this,\r\nbut please lemme call you aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Hey, wait a second!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Nope!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I'll follow ya t'the ends o' the earth, Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Please, just accept me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Let go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I ain't lettin' go!\r\nC'mon, Kiryu-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I'll do whatever y'say.\r\nI'll swear an oath!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Er, forget the oath if y'want.\r\nAll I need is t'call ya my aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "I'm beggin' ya, Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Aniki, just lemme have this.\r\nIt's life n' death to me now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "My chance with Kiyo-chan's gone\r\nfer good... Can't y'see it from my view!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Do what you want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||a03_090||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hirose-san, 'scuse me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Come in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Y'snuck outta the hospital again?\r\nYou sure 'bout this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "It's fine.\r\nThe doctor's in on the whole thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Listen. I tell them I was in a car wreck,\r\nand the insurance money starts pourin' in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Not even a scratch on me, but they'll still\r\npay me jus' to sleep at the hospital."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "This is Hirose-san, our patriarch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Back when the Omi tried t'muscle in,\r\nhe was on the frontline, lobbin' grenades."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Ain't that right, Hirose-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Well, that was years ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Hey, Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Don't stop there, y'idiot!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "U-Uh, well... Lemme tell ya\r\nabout our guest here first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "This is Kiryu-san,\r\nall the way from Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "He's gonna be comin' 'round our place,\r\nso try n' be nice t'him, please."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Your turn, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "The name's Kazuma Kiryu.\r\nIt's an honor to meet you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Y'don't need to be so formal here.\r\nWe're pretty laid back, for yakuza."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Must seem strange to a\r\nTokyo yakuza like you, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Well, actually...\r\nI'm a civilian."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Really? That so?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Coulda fooled me, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Can't say I blame ya for thinkin he's yakuza.\r\nAniki here's tough as they come, boss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "By the way, Nagumo..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "What'd ya do about that payment?\r\nWe're flat broke, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Did the big boys give\r\nyou any lip about it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "I've got a handle on that,\r\nso nothin' t'worry about, boss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah? Works for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Hey Yuta, is the Cap here?\r\nCaptain!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "I should probly check on that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Y'can come too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||a04_010||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "I gotta say, yer face is nothin'\r\nt'write home about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Don't touch me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Yer tits ain't half bad, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Please, stop!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Don't y'think?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I'm really not comfortable..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "C'mon, let 'em breathe a little."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Y'little punks. What're y'thinkin',\r\nhittin' one o' yer customers? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Y'can't get away with shit like that.\r\nI'm gonna break every last one o' ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Shut up! Don't you know when to stop!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "That's enough o' yer lip!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Hey, who're you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Can't y'see we're busy here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Jus' get lost already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Hm? HMM?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Huh? And who're you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "A customer, same as you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "I was hoping to relax here tonight. I'd like\r\nit if you showed that woman some respect."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Old man. Y'from around here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Y'don't know shit about\r\nhow this stuff goes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Now what were y'sayin' about us? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "It's him again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Wait, that's the guy Cap was callin' his aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Y'hear that? This guy thinks he can\r\nteach us some manners."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Before that, let us show ya how\r\nthings really work 'round these parts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Go.\r\nI'll be fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||a04_020||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "All right. Let's get 'im!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Owowwowow!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "This is Haruto's mom."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Apparently the picture was taken\r\nover in the bar district."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "W-Wait, she's..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "You know her?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Well, uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Hey Cap, let me see!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Ah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Sh-She's, uh... She's a lot younger\r\nthan I was expectin', that's all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Looks almost like a high schooler, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Right guys?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Huh? O-Oh yeah, totally."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "But fer real, we've never seen her before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "None of us'd forget a girl\r\nthis pretty showin' up here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Her name is Haruka Sawamura. She used\r\nto be an idol, and she was on TV a lot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "O-Ohhh!\r\nMakes sense she'd be so cute, then!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "You're sure you haven't\r\nseen her before?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Uhhh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Oh, right! I nearly forgot about\r\nthat errand the boss gave me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I gotta get goin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Hold up, what'd he ask ya t'do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Shoot, it slipped my mind again.\r\nI'll have to remember while I'm walkin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga-aniki. We've gotta go clean up\r\nat Moreno, right? C'mon, shall we?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Hm? Oh, I 'member now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Well, sorry 'bout this.\r\nWe're gonna have t'go, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga-aniki, c'mon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Well, y'know how it is.\r\nLots'a busy work in a small family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Sure seems that way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "And is your patriarch here today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "The boss?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Not sure, t'be honest.\r\nHe sneaks out the back all the time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Lemme go look fer him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "No, it's all right. Just thought\r\nI'd say hello before I head home."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||a04_030||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "R-Right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "I have reason to believe\r\nthe Hirose Family knew Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "At least, that's how it seemed\r\nwhen I showed them her picture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "But for some reason,\r\nthey chose to keep me in the dark."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Haruka-chan used to be an idol, didn't she?\r\nMaybe that's how they know her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "No. If that were it, they could\r\nhave just come out and said so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "They were definitely involved with\r\nHaruka somehow while she was here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I can't really talk,\r\nbut they're pretty bad liars."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "If they're going to lie,\r\nthey should learn to act."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "But you know, I'm not angry.\r\nAnd I don't plan on forcing it out of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "I'll wait until they're ready\r\nto tell me themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "And you're okay with that, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I actually kind of like them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "I'm heading over to Moreno now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "You mean the Hirose bar?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Yeah, the one run by that Matsunaga guy.\r\nThey're probably over there now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I don't mean to impose..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "...But could you look after Haruto again?\r\nI'd rather not run into Masuzoe with him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "I'm happy to do that whenever you need it.\r\nHaruto-kun is always welcome with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "I'll bring him back to your place tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||a04_040||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Well, I'll see you tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "What the..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "What're ya doin'!? Stay back!\r\nY'can't do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I'm the head o' the Masuzoe Family!\r\nThe Yomei Alliance fights for me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "If y'kill me, every last yakuza\r\nin Hiroshima'll be out for blood!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Quiet now, Masuzoe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "The Yomei Alliance fights for you, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Y'think you're that important?\r\nFuckin' idiot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "You must be Kiryu.\r\nNice to meet ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "And you are?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Yomei Alliance captain and patriarch of\r\nmy own family. The name's Koshimizu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "So, you're the number two\r\nman in Hiroshima?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "N-No way. Was this Kiryu-san?\r\nHe beat all these guys himself...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Holy shit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Y'think you're doing a good job\r\nof hiding your identity..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "...But to me, the dragon on yer\r\nback is plain as day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "You know who Kiryu-san is, don't ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Even fer Hiroshima, this town's tiny.\r\nShipbuilding's all it's got goin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "That said..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "With you here, this little dump\r\njust got a lot more interesting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whaddya mean by that?\r\nJus' who the hell <font_kind=yakuza_italic>is</font_kind> this guy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "The Hirose Family has\r\nalready been dealt with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Consider it my warm welcome."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Cap'n Koshimizu was talkin' crazy, right?\r\nThat stuff 'bout yer identity..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Why'd y'come?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Didn't I tell ya not to leave Moreno!?\r\nWhy couldn't y'just stay put?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Y'think this is gonna solve anythin'?\r\nNow the main family's got your scent."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Who knows what's comin' now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "I'd rather have lost my pinky n' been\r\ndone with it! Y'don't get this shit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Trust me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "I know what I'm doing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Ya goddamn turkey!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "Listen up. If y'got time to criticize\r\nKiryu-aniki, y'got time to bow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "It's 'cause of him y'still got\r\nall yer digits. Right!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga-aniki.\r\nY'didn't have t'cut yer finger off?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "They really let you off the hook."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "Wait, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "Your face is all beat to hell!\r\nThey got ya good, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "Dammit... So the main family\r\nreally did punish ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "Don't be an idiot.\r\nI'm th'one who kicked Matsunaga's ass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "I-It was you, Cap?\r\nWhy'd y'do that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "Koshimizu was here. Matsunaga'd be\r\na finger short if I didn't do somethin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "This whuppin' was all outta the\r\nkindness o' my heart. Ain't that right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "U-Uh, right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "Good. Don't worry, Kiryu-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "I made sure it looked\r\nworse than it felt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "What're y'talkin' about!? That ain't true!\r\nY'damn near killed me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||59||||4"
msgid "It was jus' punch after punch\r\nafter punch, y'brute!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||60||||4"
msgid "Y'got balls sayin' that,\r\nya ungrateful bastard!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||61||||4"
msgid "C'mere!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||62||||4"
msgid "Boss!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||63||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||64||||4"
msgid "When did ya get here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||65||||4"
msgid "I've been here the whole time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "Yer done fighting, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||a04_045||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Y'think you're doing a good job\r\nof hiding your identity..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "...But to me, the dragon on yer\r\nback is plain as day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "You know who Kiryu-san is, don't ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Even fer Hiroshima, this town's tiny.\r\nShipbuilding's all it's got goin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "That said..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "With you here, this little dump\r\njust got a lot more interesting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whaddya mean by that?\r\nJus' who the hell <font_kind=yakuza_italic>is</font_kind> this guy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "The Hirose Family has\r\nalready been dealt with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Consider it my warm welcome."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Cap'n Koshimizu was talkin' crazy, right?\r\nThat stuff 'bout yer identity..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Why'd y'come?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Didn't I tell ya not to leave Moreno!?\r\nWhy couldn't y'just stay put?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Y'think this is gonna solve anythin'?\r\nNow the main family's got your scent."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Who knows what's comin' now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I'd rather have lost my pinky n' been\r\ndone with it! Y'don't get this shit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Trust me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "I know what I'm doing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Ya goddamn turkey!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Listen up. If y'got time to criticize\r\nKiryu-aniki, y'got time to bow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "It's 'cause of him y'still got\r\nall yer digits. Right!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga-aniki.\r\nY'didn't have t'cut yer finger off?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "They really let you off the hook."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Wait, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Your face is all beat to hell!\r\nThey got ya good, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Dammit... So the main family\r\nreally did punish ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Don't be an idiot.\r\nI'm th'one who kicked Matsunaga's ass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "I-It was you, Cap?\r\nWhy'd y'do that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Koshimizu was here. Matsunaga'd be\r\na finger short if I didn't do somethin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "This whuppin' was all outta the\r\nkindness o' my heart. Ain't that right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "U-Uh, right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "Good. Don't worry, Kiryu-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "I made sure it looked\r\nworse than it felt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "What're y'talkin' about!? That ain't true!\r\nY'damn near killed me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "It was jus' punch after punch\r\nafter punch, y'brute!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "Y'got balls sayin' that,\r\nya ungrateful bastard!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "C'mere!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "Boss!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "When did ya get here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "I've been here the whole time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "Yer done fighting, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||a04_050||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Nagumo. In that case..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "...Do you know if Haruto's\r\ndad is here in town?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I couldn't say fer sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Everyone loved Haruka-san,\r\nbut I never heard o' her datin' anyone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "And the baby's 'bout a year old, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Haruka-san musta got pregnant jus'\r\nas she was shippin' out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "It was probly a year n' a half ago by now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I haven't heard o' anyone who's\r\nseen her since."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Even now, it's hard t'believe Haruto-kun's\r\nreally her kid. It jus' don't add up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "That's all me n' my family know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Although, maybe I could point ya to\r\nsomeone who knows more 'bout her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Who?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Well, Haruka-san was workin' to support\r\nherself here. At a bar over in town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "I'm sure ya know the place, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Snack Kiyomi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "If anyone was close\r\nto Haruka-san 'round here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||a04_060||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "...It was Kiyo-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Ahhhhhh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Y'freakin' dumbbell!\r\nDon't yell like that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Yer gonna scare the baby!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "But he already messed the diaper I just\r\ngave him! Why won't he stop shitting!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "That jus' shows he's a healthy kid!\r\nNow go on and get another one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Hi there! Peekaboo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "This is hopeless!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "A face like that ain't gonna stop\r\na baby from cryin', Cap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What's that s'posed t'mean!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Give it a rest already, would you!?\r\nJust go away and let me deal with this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "'Scuse me!? Y'can't talk to yer captain\r\nlike that! I'll pulverize ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Well look at that.\r\nYer actually gettin' the hang of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Only cause y'make me do this so much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Okay, all done! There we go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Dammit... Why's he still crying?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Bring him here, Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Whoa. I guess he's jus' the calmest\r\nwhen he's in yer arms, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Maybe so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||a05_010||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Though if I had to guess, he'd probably\r\nrather be with his mother instead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||a05_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Haruka..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "So, do you know who\r\nHaruto's father is?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry. I don't."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "It never seemed like Haruka-chan was\r\ndating anyone when she worked at the bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I do have an idea, though.\r\nI'm not totally sure, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You do? Who are you thinking?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Well<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Heyyy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "This is the last place I expected to find you,\r\nyet here you are, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Someya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "What are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "I could ask the same of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "As for me, I've been staying\r\nat that hotel right over there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "It's my first trip to the countryside.\r\nClimbing all these hills is a real pain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "That's not what I'm asking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "I want to know why a Tojo Clan\r\npatriarch is out here in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Easy now, it's nothing you need\r\nto put up your fists about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I'm here to swear an oath. Between myself\r\nand the Yomei Alliance's Koshimizu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "I already know what you're thinking.\r\nToo much disparity in our ranks, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "It's true. A mere family patriarch is no\r\nequal to Hiroshima's number two man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Under normal circumstances, the oath would\r\nbe between the chairmen, Dojima and Kurusu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "But as you know,\r\nhe's been indisposed with trials."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Even so, why would it be you here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Excellent question, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Acting Chairman Sugai is considering me\r\nfor the role of successor to the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "You, a Tojo Clan chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "As Koshimizu is the Yomei Alliance successor,\r\nwe can swear this oath as complete equals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "I get the sense you don't approve."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Perhaps you're interested in coming back\r\nto swear it in my place, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "I wouldn't object.\r\nFate seems to be pulling us together anyway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Fate?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Our meeting all the way out here\r\nis more than just coincidence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "And that woman beside you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "She used to be with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "It's good to see you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Kiyomi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "I should have known you'd come back here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "I looked everywhere for you after you left.\r\nI must say, it's good to see you're safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "I looked everywhere for you after you left.\r\nI must say, it's good to see you're safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Look at the time!\r\nI should be getting back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "Well then, Fourth Chairman..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "If you'll excuse us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||a05_030||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "I looked everywhere for you after you left.\r\nI must say, it's good to see you're safe."
msgstr ""

