msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "And that woman beside you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "She used to be with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "It's good to see you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Kiyomi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "I should have known you'd come back here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "I looked everywhere for you after you left.\r\nI must say, it's good to see you're safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "I looked everywhere for you after you left.\r\nI must say, it's good to see you're safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Look at the time!\r\nI should be getting back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Well then, Fourth Chairman..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "If you'll excuse us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||a05_035||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "I looked everywhere for you after you left.\r\nI must say, it's good to see you're safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Y-Y-Y'gotta be kiddin' me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Who's this Someya bastard anyways?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Well Kiyomi <font_kind=yakuza_italic>did</font_kind> say she used\r\nt'live in Tokyo, didn't she?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "She's even got that Tokyo accent.\r\nMaybe she dated the guy or somethin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Y'think they used to be married!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Dumbass! Y'implyin' Kiyo-chan\r\nis divorced!? Ain't no way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "How would you know!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "It's freakin' obvious! The name Kiyomi's\r\ns'posed t'represent purity and beauty!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Pure women get married too, man! Besides,\r\nwouldn't her getting divorced make sense?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Why else would someone her age come all\r\nthe way back here jus' to open a bar!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Yer wrong. I bet a pretty girl like Kiyo-chan\r\njus' couldn't handle all the Tokyo pollution."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah. She's pretty good at lookin' after\r\nkids, too. Ain't that right, Kiryu-aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Huh? Uh, I suppose she is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Y'think she has a kid of her own?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "You asswipe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "A real woman can take care o'kids\r\neven if she ain't got her own!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "You buttheads wanna keep talkin' shit\r\nor do I gotta bust ya!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "You know this is all speculation, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Don't blow it out of proportion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "A-Aniki... I know yer right,\r\nbut I jus' can't calm m'self down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "And if that guy's a yakuza,\r\nit's even worse."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Y'guys! Help!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Ino? What's goin' on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||a05_040||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "It's Kiyo-chan...\r\nShe just got nabbed!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "These are..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "...Masks?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "They're shady is what they are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Why d'ya even have these, boss?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I used to wear 'em if I wanted\r\nto beat the crap outta someone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Usually guys from the main family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "They never got wise, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Maybe, but there probly weren't too many\r\nthugs runnin' around in ski masks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I bet they had some guesses."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Here y'go.\r\nThis one's yers, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Huh? No way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "I'm not big on hiding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Whaddya mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "The Yomei Alliance knows you've been\r\nhangin' around with us, Kiryu-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "If they see you there,\r\nthey'll ID us fer sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Aniki. We don't got time t'be\r\nwafflin' around 'bout this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Fine then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||a05_050||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Let's do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||a05_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||a05_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Wh-Who're you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||a05_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "C'mon out! Get ready fer\r\na righteous ass whoopin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Aniki.\r\nLooks like that Someya guy ain't here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Guess we still gotta look in there, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "This shit's intense.\r\nWhat kinda room is this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "It's too freakin' hot!\r\nSorry, I gotta get outta here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Ahhh, that's better!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "The hell is this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "That you, Nagumo!?\r\nWhaddya think yer doin'!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Yer wrong!\r\nI totally ain't Nagumo...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Yer dumb as rocks!\r\nIt's too late t'hide!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Awww hell!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Oh really?\r\nIs that you, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Someya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Looks like we can't write this\r\nmeeting off as coincidence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "And what's with that outfit?\r\nAren't you hot in that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Kiyomi better be safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Where are you hiding her!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "I can't believe our fourth chairman would\r\nstoop so low over one woman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "The rumors about you were right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "I asked you where the girl is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Give me a straight answer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I see now. You want to fight me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately for you,\r\nI'm not interested."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Your little raid has me at a disadvantage.\r\nI'm not dumb enough to fight you head on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "You know, I've made it this far\r\nbecause I only fight on sure bets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "You're saying you're a coward, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Let's not jump to any conclusions.\r\nI haven't lost this fight just yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "You know what they say, don't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Live to fight another day!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "Bastard!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||a05_070||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Dammit. Get back here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Someya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "No more running!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Look what you've done. I only just took\r\na bath, and I'm covered in sweat again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I'll have to take another one later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I see you've yet to get any ink done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "In this day and age, tattoos are\r\nnothing but a hindrance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "We no longer live in a world where\r\nyakuza shake down civilians for cash."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Working an honest job is a far safer\r\nalternative, really. Pays better, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "That's what the leadership teaches now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Tattoos aren't supposed to be threats."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "They represent the ideals\r\nof the life you've chosen to lead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "You think a few drops of ink\r\nreally carry that much weight?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Stop dreaming."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "The real world is a harsh mistress."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "If a worker wants to please his boss,\r\nhe raises profits, wouldn't you agree?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "So if tats are going to hurt your bottom line,\r\nthe modern yakuza is right to avoid them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "If profits have become more important than\r\nthe dream, then the yakuza are finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "A clan only survives because there's a guy\r\nwith ideals worth following on his back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "If the weaker members don't see strength\r\nat the top, they'll start drifting away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Funny you say that. Money is what's kept new\r\nrecruits coming our way these past years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "At least, Sugai-san seems to think so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "But it's fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "If you want Kiyomi, she's in there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "My men are probably enjoying\r\ntheir time with her as we speak."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Keep the lies to yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "All I needed was her location."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Now let's get this over with\r\nso I can get her out of here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "That won't be as easy as you think."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "If I'm facing the legendary fourth chairman..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||a05_080||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "I'll need to show proper respect.\r\nI won't hold anything back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Everythin' okay here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "What's this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "That you, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Oh, and Hirose's imbecile's here, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Koshimizu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "We've been expectin' ya.\r\nCome on in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Kiyo-chan! Are y'okay!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "What are you two doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Koshimizu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Can you explain this interference?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "President Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Iwami?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "We've come to take Kiyomi home."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "We were told she was being held\r\nhere against her will."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Held? And who told ya that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "We were just extendin' our\r\nhospitality to our guest's wife here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Wh-What're y'talkin' about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Ah, that was a lovely pre-dinner\r\nworkout. Thanks, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Kiyomi's, well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "She's my ex-wife."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "You used to be married?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Is this true, Kiyomi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "He's makin' it up!\r\nHe's gotta be!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "N-No..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "It was a surprise findin' Someya-san's ex-wife\r\nin this little town, but fate's funny like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "So we invited her up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "It's clear this is a misunderstanding.\r\nHowever, there must still be consequences."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Wouldn't you say, Koshimizu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "Yeah, absolutely."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Consider the Hirose Family cut off from the Yomei Alliance.\r\nYer patriarch's cuttin' off a finger, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Hold on a sec!\r\nHirose-san didn't do nothin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Shut yer mouth!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "Someya-san here came all the way from\r\nTokyo t'swear an oath with us, as our guest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Y'think a finger even makes up for this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "That's enough, Koshimizu-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "This was meant to be a celebration.\r\nYou're scaring Kiyomi-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "Let's bury the hatchet for today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "But Chairman..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "Listen closely. When I say to forget it,\r\nyou forget it. Do I make myself clear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "Yes, I understand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "And you, Someya-san?\r\nYou don't mind, do you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "Of course not. I caused this\r\nmisunderstanding to begin with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "And you are?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "The chairman of Iwami Shipbuilding.\r\nMy name is Heizo Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "Chairman Iwami leads the Iwami Group,\r\nwhich in turn heads up Iwami Shipbuilding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "He also goes by another name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "Takeru Kurusu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "Kurusu..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "Chairman of the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "Takeru Kurusu is the name he uses\r\nfor all yakuza operations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||59||||4"
msgid "So the head of Iwami Shipbuilding\r\nis also the chairman of the Yomei Alliance?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||60||||4"
msgid "Nowadays it would be more accurate to say\r\nthe Iwami Group is a \"front\" for the Yomei."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||61||||4"
msgid "This is my son, Tsuneo.\r\nHe acts as president of Iwami Shipbuilding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||62||||4"
msgid "It's a pleasure to meet you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||63||||4"
msgid "My name is K<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||64||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||65||||4"
msgid "The Tojo Clan's fourth chairman, yes?\r\nI'm quite familiar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "However, it seems this is\r\nno place for us to speak."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "Why don't we go elsewhere?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||a05_090||cinema_telop||68||||4"
msgid "Fine by me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hey, those masks work out okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "They didn't catch on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Well, Captain Nagumo got too hot\r\nn' ripped his off partway through."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "We went through all that fer nothin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "What happened t'you, Nagumo?\r\nY'gotta sack up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Kiyo-chan..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I... I can't believe it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What's his problem?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Forget it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Here, lemme show you guys\r\nthe right way to use a mask."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Tagashira, get over here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Mama. Shouldn't you be at the bar?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "I wanted to wait for you.\r\nWe never finished talking about Haruka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Maybe not, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "How are you doing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I'm okay now. Just a little shaken\r\nafter everything that happened."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Understandable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "The masks're good, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Hey, boss... They're kinda\r\nin the middle of somethin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Uh, don't mind us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Anyway, we were talking about\r\nwho Haruto-kun's dad might be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Right. You said you have\r\nan idea of who he is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||a05_110||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Huh? Do you really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki. Kamurocho..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "I wanna go with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I can't let Tatsukawa go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "That son of a bitch. He's gonna pay\r\nfer what he did to Haruka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I won't be able to sleep until I\r\nbeat the shit out of him myself!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "All right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I'm goin', too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Y'are, Cap? Why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "It's too painful for him to stay here.\r\nPretty obvious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "That's what a broken heart does, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Um, I should probably get going then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||a06_010||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "This works out fine. Might even be a nice\r\nchange of pace in Kamurocho with you two."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "So this is Kamurocho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "That dumbass Tatsukawa. What was\r\nhe thinkin' coming to a city like this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Yuta, it's yer first time in Tokyo, yeah?\r\nY'ain't even been outta Hiroshima before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Try not to embarrass us now, y'hear!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Don't let bein' a country bumpkin\r\nmake ya an easy mark."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Hey, you can't smoke on the street."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "You can't just walk and smoke nowadays.\r\nYou need to go somewhere private."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Oh, you fer real with that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Please try not to embarrass us, Cap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Ya shitstick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Well, do you want to go for a smoke\r\nbefore we look for Tatsukawa?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "There's a café near here called Alps."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Y'really wanna go to some\r\nregular ol' coffee shop t'smoke?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "We're in Kamurocho, ain't we?\r\nLet's go someplace with booze! N' ladies!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||a06_020||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "What're you talking about, Cap?\r\nWe're not here to mess around, y'know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hey, it's him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "He's the guy who tossed\r\nYuta outta that club."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Hey! The yakiniku's great here, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "The smell is to die for. And isn't\r\nthe meat perfect in every way?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Sorry to interrupt your meal.\r\nI'm the proprietor of Stardust."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "The name's Joon-gi Han."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "As I hear it, you graced my club\r\nwith your presence earlier today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Only to have this imbecile\r\nturn you away at the door!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Wh-What the hell're y'doin'!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "If you'd be interested, can I\r\nmake up for his discourtesy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||a06_030||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||a06_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "The hell is this place...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||a06_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Aniki. Are all host clubs like this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||a06_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Quite a vulgar place, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||a06_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "But I must say, this stimulation is\r\nexactly what Stardust was missing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||a06_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "They even call it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||a06_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "The Eden of Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Enough!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "I'm not quite finished yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Yuta's done everything he can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "For every punch you threw,\r\nhe never turned his back on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "If you want proof of his strength,\r\nhe's already given it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Stop it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I'll fight you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "You're after me, aren't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Very well. In that case..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Let us proceed to the main event."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "You were very effective bait, friend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "By making the Dragon of Dojima kneel to me,\r\nI'll bring the Jingweon into a new epoch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "We will finally forget our grudges of the\r\npast and push forward into the modern era."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Maybe so.\r\nBut you'll have to defeat me first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "It seems age has clouded your vision."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "A new dawn is fast approaching.\r\nThe time of Kazuma Kiryu is over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "My heart races at the thought of being\r\nthe one to bring closure to your legend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I don't care what you say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "But... I won't let you forget\r\nyour promise, Joon-gi Han."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "You mean about Tatsukawa?\r\nOf course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Unlike you spineless yakuza, I take\r\nquite a bit of pride in my sportsmanship."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Once our fight is over, I will be\r\nglad to tell you everything I know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "All I ask is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "...Don't hold anything back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "You don't need to worry about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Everyone here will bear witness.\r\nThe dragon of legend shall be put to rest!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Go, go, go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||a06_050||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "I love you, Han-sama!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||a06_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Show's over, Joon-gi Han."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||a06_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "A-Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||a06_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||a06_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Get your fucking hands off of him!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "What's up with these rooms?\r\nFeels like nobody's here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Yer right about that. There ain't\r\neven nameplates on the doors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "What about that one?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Go fer it, Yuta.\r\nTake a little peek inside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "It's open."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Jus' go already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "What'd y'see?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What the...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "It's Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Y-Yer kiddin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "No way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||a06_070||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "But... Why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||a07_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hm? I don't recall having\r\nany appointments today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||a07_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "You are?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||a07_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Who do you think?\r\nYou can't put the pieces together?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||a07_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Ah, now I see.\r\nI do know that voice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||a07_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||a07_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "The Dragon of Dojima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||a07_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I'm in need of some answers...\r\nAnd I'll do what it takes to get them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||a07_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "We need to talk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "[D-Dammit! How could we let\r\nthese fucking whelps humiliate us!?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki. This is Ed?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Yeah. He's the one who killed Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Ed. Just answer this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "What was Tatsukawa really like?\r\nWhy did you kill him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "How exactly did he betray you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "You don't know when to quit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Answer me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Bastards... I'll murder you all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "And what if I kill you first!? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "That's... M-Masuzoe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Masuzoe?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "K-Kiryu-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I gotta say..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "This is a real pain in the ass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||a07_030||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "The four o' you really made\r\na mess outta this one..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Should you be showing yourself here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I am the head of the Saio Triad.\r\nYou may call me Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "So you're the boss of\r\nthis organization?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Indeed. I've heard a great deal\r\nabout you from Masuzoe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Every yakuza in the country acknowledges\r\nthe strength you possess, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "You are the Dragon of Dojima, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "What could a man like yourself have wanted\r\nout in Onomichi? I'm very much intrigued."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "[Lower your guns.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I recognize that this meeting has not\r\ncome at the best of times for either of us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "However, I believe we can still\r\nsalvage a beneficial relationship."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Once you have calmed down a bit,\r\nI would like to meet with you again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Tomorrow night.\r\nIt will be only the two of us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I would be glad to give answers\r\nto several of your questions there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "That's a good deal for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "But tell me, what do you get out of it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "First off, I don't have to sully the fine\r\nwood floors of this place with your blood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "There is more to it than that, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "At the moment, we are at war with the Tojo Clan.\r\nThe Yomei Alliance is also involved, as you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "You have the ability to speak to the leaders\r\nof both organizations equally, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "There is great value in\r\nmy showing you hospitality."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Do you accept my invitation?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I get it.\r\nTomorrow, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Meet him in the ruins of a\r\nbrothel called Shangri-La."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||a07_035||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Remember... The boss\r\nonly invited you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "What's the latest on the Tojo Clan's\r\nlittle war in Kamurocho?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "How long is it going to drag on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "It's already nearly over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I know it's caused a great deal of tension\r\nin Kanto. You have my sympathies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "It's nice to be wined-and-dined like this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "...But if the triads keep fucking with us,\r\nwe're gonna get laughed at in Kansai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Kamurocho is the heart of Kanto's yakuza.\r\nWe need it to be stable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "He's right. All we're really asking here\r\nis that you rising stars do your part."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "And we will, Senpai. I'm grateful to even\r\nhave a seat at the same table as you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "I've also heard rumblings that the\r\nDragon of Dojima is back in Kamurocho?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Indeed. Word travels fast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "You can't let a civilian keep walking\r\naround like he owns the place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "This is the dawn of your time at\r\nthe head of the clan, Someya-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Tell that washed-up old fuck to\r\ncrawl back into his hole."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Old fuck?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "You heard me. Maybe he was great\r\nonce, but those days are long gone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "It's the present that makes the man,\r\nnot the past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "There's no place for a puffed-up\r\nhas-been like him anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Hey, give it a rest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||a08_005||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "The hell!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "So you're trying to tell me\r\nwe both want the same thing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Indeed. Am I wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "You're even more naive than I thought."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "If what you just said is true, you're the\r\nreason Daigo is behind bars right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You know, he was only a child\r\nwhen we first met."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "And after he left the yakuza, it was me who\r\ndragged him back to become the sixth chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Interesting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "In other words, you have no interest\r\nin forming an alliance with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "I may have left the clan years ago,\r\nbut I'm still yakuza."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Anyone who'd dare to harm someone\r\nI care about... is going to pay the price."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "That shouldn't come as a surprise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Your ability to succeed with such\r\nminimal planning... It's impressive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "By defeating me in front of Lo-san, you could\r\npotentially earn the trust of the Saio Triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "It wouldn't be the first time your integrity\r\nhas charmed men who were once your foes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "It's that charisma that helped you\r\nascend the ranks all those years ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I only seek the same for myself,\r\nthough my methods are more calculated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "What are you trying to say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "You and I aren't so different.\r\nJust different means to the same end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Don't flatter yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "This should be a fascinating sight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "So the fourth chairman is going to\r\ngrace me with the honor of a duel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I won't be needing this, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "This time, I won't hold anything back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Neither will I."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||a08_020||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||a08_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "You're truly...\r\nthe Dragon of Dojima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||a08_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Looks like I'm finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||a08_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "No matter how hard I struggle,\r\nI'll never be able to escape you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||a08_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "So! Who gets to finish me off?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||a08_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Will it be you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||a08_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Or perhaps you, Lo-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Apologies, but I cannot offer you\r\nany knowledge of Tatsukawa's betrayal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Though it might be different if you joined\r\nthe Saio Triad by swearing allegiance to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "But in truth, you have no need to learn\r\nthe details of Tatsukawa's death."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "The reason for that being..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "...He is not Haruto Sawamura's father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Someone else is the father.\r\nI assure you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I don't understand.\r\nHow could you possibly know that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Do you have information on Haruka, too!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "All I can say now is, that child bears great\r\nsignificance to this war in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Furthermore..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "...It seems others are slowly becoming\r\naware of his true value."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "What value are you talking about?\r\nWho the hell is this kid's father!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "You may want to answer that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "The child's situation is becoming\r\nmore pressing than you realize."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-aniki! It's Yuta!\r\nSomethin' happened in Hiroshima!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "I jus' got a call from Kiyomi-san.\r\nIt has to do with the boss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Apparently he disappeared with Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Why would Hirose take Haruto!?\r\nWhat's going on here!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I have no idea!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Hello? Aniki?\r\nAre you still there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Hello!? Aniki!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Yuta. Pack for Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||a08_035||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "We're leaving now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Someya-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Wh-What happened to you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "That bastard won't be leeching\r\noff you anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I took care of things."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You'll never have to see him again.\r\nHe won't be coming back to Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Your debt's been cleared, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "You're free."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Be more careful, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "At your age, you should know better."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "You did that for me...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||a09_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "But why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "I don't even have the right to call\r\nmyself her mother at this point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "What're y'talkin' about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "That's a load o' bull."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "How can y'really be that stupid, huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Y'think this is about the <font_kind=yakuza_italic>right</font_kind>!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Y'gave her life! She's still yer daughter.\r\nQuit pretendin' that don't mean anythin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Nagumo-kun..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Y'did the only thing y'could to get away\r\nfrom that bastard husband o' yers!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Fer real, though. If y'wanna get her back\r\nfrom Someya, I'll do whatever it takes t'help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Yer daughter's gonna love ya\r\nno matter what happened before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "That's why y'don't get to quit bein'\r\nher parent. I ain't gonna let ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Sorry 'bout that, Kiyo-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "But stuff like that's better comin'\r\nfrom an ol' buddy like me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Y'gotta find a way to make things right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Thank you, Nagumo-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I needed to hear that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||a09_020||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "I've been hoping someone would say that\r\nto me ever since I came back to this town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||a09_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "D'ya ever stop t'think about whose\r\nbackyard yer trespassin' in?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||a09_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||a09_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Koshimizu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||a09_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "It's time I give ya a taste\r\no' what Hiroshima's really about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||a09_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "It's an honor to square off\r\n'gainst the Dragon o' Dojima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||a09_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I don't fight 'less it's gonna be good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "K-Kiryu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "This ain't over yet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I think you're about to see otherwise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "What the heck, Aniki!? Why'd ya go n' say that?\r\nKoshimizu totally saw my face!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Too late now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "How'd you guys know to come here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "The lady over at Snack Hourglass\r\ntold us. Boss loves that place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Anyway, we should try to\r\nwake Koshimizu up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "I have some questions for him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "That won't be necessary."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Let Koshimizu have his little nap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "He can't tell ya much anyway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||a09_040||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. I have answers\r\nto all of yer questions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Patriarch Hirose..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "If what you're saying is true..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "...You must know who Haruto's\r\nfather actually is, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "He's a guy y'know pretty\r\nwell, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Everyone here knows him, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "So here's yer answer..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "No way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "You?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Yuta Usami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "It's been under yer noses all along."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||a09_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "You are Haruto Sawamura's father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Stop it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Wh-What are you doing, Yuta-kun?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Wait, this is the customer from last night."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Why would you do something like this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "He's one of those tabloid snakes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "This guy has been tracking you\r\nfer a while, Haruka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "You don't want people taking\r\npictures of you, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Even if folks won't come out n' say it,\r\nwe all know who you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "And we know the last thing you want\r\nis to get spotted by the media."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "You knew we were onto ya, didn't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Captain Nagumo ain't exactly\r\nan award-winning actor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "But this won't change anything.\r\nWe'll keep acting like we don't know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Everyone in this town loves you\r\nfor who you are, Haruka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Yuta-kun..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "It might be awkward for me to\r\nshow up 'round Kiyomi-san's now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "But still..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||a10_010||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I hope I'll see you around town\r\nstill, Haruka-chan. Yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Yuta Usami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "It's been under yer noses all along.\r\nYou are Haruto Sawamura's father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "F-For real?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Yuta! Why didn't y'say anythin'!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "We need answers! C'mon!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Forgive me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "So you and Haruka..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Y'couldn'ta mentioned this sooner,\r\nya slippery fuck!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Ya know it don't exactly happen by accident!\r\nSo c'mon..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Out with it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Everyone was saying Tatsukawa was\r\nthe father. I didn't think it could be me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Hey, hold on a sec, Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "When y'were with Haruka-chan, uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Y'didn't think to bag it up?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "C'mon, Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "It ain't true, right?\r\nJus' tell me it's a lie n' it'll all go away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Th-Things just kinda happened..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I mean, we only did it once!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "How did one time..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Y'fuckin' jackass!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Stop."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "This is neither the time or place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Patriarch. This isn't making sense."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "If Yuta himself didn't know he was\r\nHaruto's dad, how can you be so sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Th-That's a good point!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "It's sorta hard to explain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Wouldn't you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Wh-What the hell!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "You..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Masuzoe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "What are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Masuzoe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Hirose-san. You better keep your promise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "If I do this for you, neither the Saio\r\nnor the Yomei will take me back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "If you abandon me now,\r\nI'll have nowhere left to run."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "Just spill the beans already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "You can escape to wherever you want.\r\nChairman Kurusu will make sure of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "I-I don't think I'm followin'..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||a10_020||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "What the hell's goin' on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "You're well aware of what happened next."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "The Saio Triad killed Tatsukawa after they\r\ncaught him trying to sell the baby to Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Did you see what they did to him!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "They didn't even spare his girl.\r\nEd made Tatsukawa watch as he butchered her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "He actually laughed about it\r\nwhen he told me the story."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Ed took his sweet time with the girl,\r\nthen slit Tatsukawa's throat as a mercy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I know I've sworn lifelong allegiance\r\nto the Saio Triad, but I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Who knows when I might end up in\r\nthe same boat as Tatsukawa now!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What're y'cryin' about?\r\nYou deserve as much, y'shithead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "That's everything I know, Hirose-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "You promised... Chairman Kurusu will\r\nmake sure they can't get to me, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Hang onta the kid real tight now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "They're comin' fer Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Shit! Who the hell're these guys!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "All of you stand back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Keep Hirose-san and Haruto safe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||a10_030||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "G-Got it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "A-Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Shit, what do I do!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Cap, toss Haruto t'me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Nagumo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Sorry 'bout this, kid!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You all get into the town!\r\nProtect Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "[He's getting away!\r\nCatch him!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Pass 'im!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "[Stand down.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "[This one's mine.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "It's you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Joon-gi Han!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "What are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Fine..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Then get out of my way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||a10_040||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "I said move!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Get off yer ass, Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Y'hear me?\r\nThis ain't the time to kick yerself!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Have it yer way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "A-Aniki...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Only one of us deserves to hit him now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "And that's me, Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Care to guess what I'm\r\nupset about right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "It's not what you did with Haruka,\r\nor the fact that you hid it from us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Well then? What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Before today,\r\nif a baby had been kidnapped..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "...You would've risked your life to\r\nsave him without a second thought."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Nagumo and the others, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "But it's different now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Why can't you bring yourself\r\nto help him anymore?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Is it because you found out\r\nyou have a triad's blood?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Or is it because you know Haruto\r\nshares that same bloodline?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "In the end, it doesn't matter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "So don't let something so shallow..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "...Make you act like less of a father!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Aniki..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Blood shouldn't change\r\nhow you live your life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "And it damn well shouldn't\r\nchange how you judge others."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "If you can't see past that,\r\nthen you're no better than Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "As for me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Even if it kills me,\r\nI'm bringing Haruto back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "You can stay here\r\nsulking for all I care."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "If that's your choice..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Don't ever let me see you again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "I'm outta here, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||a10_050||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Aniki said all I wanted t'say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "All right! We can push off\r\nwhenever y'want, Nagumo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Hold on a sec."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I'm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Please take me with you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I'm begging you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Yuta..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I wanna help save him!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "When they took him away,\r\nI lost all hope."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "It seemed like we'd never get him back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "That's why I was such a coward!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Y'know I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I can't tell you how many times\r\nI've changed Haruto's diaper."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "How many times he got shit\r\nn' piss all over me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "But every time..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "...He'd give me the brightest little smile."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I don't know what I'd do\r\nif I couldn't see that smile again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Haruto's..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Haruto is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "...My son!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "So please!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "You have to let me come with you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Of course y'can! Get yer ass on\r\nthe boat and let's go, buttwipe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "That cool, Aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Don't be ridiculous."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||a10_060||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "How could I say no to him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||a10_070||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "[The girl escaped?\r\nWhat the hell is Tatsukawa doing!?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Sorry for the wait, Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "K-Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "It seems... I was right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I always knew it would be worth\r\nputting my pride on the line to fight you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "If you choose to kill me now,\r\nI'd have no complaints."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "The kid doesn't need to see\r\nwhat I'd do to you, actually."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "How can you continue to be so naive?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "None of your enemies care about that child.\r\nNot Tsuneo Iwami, and not Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "They will come at you with everything\r\nthey have to get their hands on him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Though knowing you, you'll just keep\r\nfighting them to find your answers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Who knows, you may even uncover\r\nthe secret of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "The secret of Onomichi again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "What exactly is this secret?\r\nAnd who's keeping it hidden?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "You'll have to speak to Chairman Kurusu\r\nof the Yomei Alliance for that answer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Fact is, he's the one who holds\r\nthe truth to the big mystery."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||a10_090||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "The source of Hiroshima's power is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||a11_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "[You know who I am, right?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||a11_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "[I'm here for my father.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||a11_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "[If he's not here...\r\nI can wait inside.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||a11_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "[Spread your arms.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||a11_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "[Hands off.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||a11_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "[I need more booze than\r\nthis to talk to that bastard.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||a11_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Yo, bio-dad.\r\nCare for a drink?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||a11_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Shit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||a11_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||a11_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "[That's Kiryu! Stop him!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||a11_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "[We can't let a yakuza inside!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||a11_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "[Stay back!\r\nWe'll kill you!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||a11_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You're in the way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||a11_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Move it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "You did this to Lo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Aren't you impressed?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I owe it all to you, Aniki.\r\nYou helped me see this shit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Don't tell me... You really planned\r\nto die here with Lo, Yuta?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "You think that will fix anything!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "If Lo and I die here, nobody will\r\nhave to come for Haruto anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "It'll all be over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "So you're not gonna listen.\r\nIs that what you're saying?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||a11_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "That's right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Yo, bio-dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Care for a drink?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "So, it appears you've learned the truth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I found out how you're trying\r\nto murder Haruto, you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Just like Masuzoe.\r\nYou kill him to shut him up?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Masuzoe is dead...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Well?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Why have you come here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I already told you that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "I want you to join me for a drink."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Gasoline?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna make sure you Saio bastards\r\ngive up on me and Haruto for good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I'd rather die than keep living as\r\nthe heir to this bullshit triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "So you plan to kill me\r\nand yourself in the process?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "How shortsighted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "If you had simply chosen to negotiate,\r\nnobody would have to die here today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I didn't come to negotiate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "I'm too dumb for that, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "There's only one thing I can do now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||a11_050||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "I'm going to die here\r\nto keep my son safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Just get out of here already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "You don't need to be a part of this, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "If you die here, what happens to Haruto!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "He'll be able to live in peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "With me and Lo dead,\r\nthe Saio Triad goes up for grabs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "They can kill each other over it for all I care.\r\nThe boy won't need to be involved."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "That's not what I asked you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "It's Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "You're really gonna let him\r\ngrow up without a father!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "I'm asking you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "This is my last request, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "As for Haruto and Haruka-chan..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Can I leave them to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I mean..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "They don't need a punk like me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Especially when they could have you inst<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I won't let you abandon them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "You're not dying over something so stupid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "We're all leaving alive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Don't mess this up for me, Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "This is the only way I can save Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Fine then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "...I'll have to drag you out by force."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "And if you insist on getting in my way,\r\nI'll do what it takes to stop you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Even by force."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "I already decided, this is\r\nthe place where I die."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "I made this choice like a man.\r\nAnd then I made peace with it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Nobody can stop me now, Aniki.\r\nNot even you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "You're being selfish.\r\nThis is bigger than just you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Think about your family!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||a11_060||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Sorry about this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "I know you're a busy man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Hirose-san, was it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "You're a grandfather now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Figured it'd be nice for you t'see\r\nyer grandson's face once in a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I assume that's not why you're here, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "You wish to speak of\r\nthe secret of Onomichi, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "You're sharper than I thought."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Truth is, killing you would be\r\nthe easiest way outta this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "But Chairman Kurusu's willing t'let you live.\r\nIf you leave Japan, that is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "The chairman and I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "We're both tired o' bloodshed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "The Saio Triad has poured a hefty sum of\r\nmoney into this location in Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "We have yet to recoup our investment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "So ya don't plan on leaving?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Consider the actions of Kurusu's son."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "He murdered the heir to our triad, Jimmy Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "As a businessman and as a father..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "...I have no reason to accept your request."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "I half expected you'd say that.\r\nSo I've got a deal for ya instead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "And that is?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Do you plan on killing the child before\r\nmy eyes to convince me to leave?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "I'll give you Yuta Usami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "I can convince him to take\r\nthe reins of the Saio Triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "How's that sound?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Oh, and if you don't accept..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "...I'll tell Yuta everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "About how this kid here's his son."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "About how you wanna murder him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "He'll want less than nothin'\r\nto do with you after that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Your precious bloodline\r\nwill come to an end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "And I know how much\r\nyou value that blood stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "That what you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "What will you do with the child?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "I'll keep him safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "I'll make it so that Yuta could never\r\npossibly know about his existence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "To be honest, I don't see why I shouldn't\r\nsilence both you and the child here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Wanna try that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "I promise you'll be the dead one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "Don't think I'll spare yer men, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Every last one of 'em, dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "You overestimate your ability."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "My subordinates all carry firearms."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "Y'think I care what they're packing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "I didn't expect Kurusu to have\r\nsuch a reptile in his den."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "Oh, and those two goons y'have watchin'\r\nmy hideout... Tatsukawa n' Masuzoe?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "Pull 'em off me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "The Saio Triad's days\r\nin Kamurocho are numbered."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "You have one month."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "As fer the secret of Onomichi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "I've lost track of how many men\r\nI've killed to protect it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "Some were my friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "Some were my aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "If you go and reveal it all now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "...You'd be disrespecting their memory."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "I'm sure it sounds quite strange to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "I was in my compound guarded by\r\nover a hundred able men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||a11_070||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "And yet, a single old man with a gun\r\nforced me to accept his terms."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "After my negotiations with Hirose\r\nconcluded..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "...I immediately retracted the order I had given\r\nfor Masuzoe and Tatsukawa to kill the child."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "However, Tsuneo Iwami had already\r\nsunk his fangs into Tatsukawa by then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Then came the hit-and-run in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "And the child slipped through Hirose's fingers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "He likely thought he had lost\r\nhis sole bargaining chip."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Hence, there was only one way for him\r\nto ensure the secret of Onomichi stayed safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "He needed me dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "And you're saying Patriarch Hirose turned\r\nYuta against you to do that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Is it not obvious?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Who was the one who told you\r\nthat Yuta is the child's father?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "And who revealed that Masuzoe\r\nand Tatsukawa wanted the child dead?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "One more thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I expect Hirose murdered Masuzoe\r\nonce he was no longer of use to him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "The longer you thrive in the underworld..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "...The more bound you become to ideals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I was bound to blood law."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "For Kurusu and Hirose..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "...It's the secret of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "That's what drives Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "He even sacrificed Yuta,\r\none of his own."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "That is how low he could sink."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "You think I'm gonna believe that!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "He'd never."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "This is bullshit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "There is only one road to the truth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Which is?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Reveal the secret of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "That will bring the nature of\r\nHiroshima's true authority to light."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "But be warned..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "If you do this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "...No amount of preparation\r\nwill be enough to face it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "Yuta Usami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "The fact is, he is the one who holds\r\nthe truth to the mystery of which we speak."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||a11_080||cinema_telop||68||||4"
msgid "The source of Hiroshima's power is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "What do you think?\r\nQuite a view, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "These flames should serve as\r\nproof of our dedication to the cause."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Gentlemen, lasting prosperity is\r\nnow within arm's reach."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Shall we toast to that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Lo-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I'm pleased with our progress thus far."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "And we have Jimmy to thank."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "You have a worthy heir."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "President Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "It's not often that my father compliments me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "However..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "...Perhaps today will be different."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "[Father.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "[You see that burning district\r\nthey call Little Asia?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "[It now belongs to the Saio Triad.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "[Jimmy. You shouldn't have gone\r\nbehind my back on this.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "[What?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "[I explicitly forbade you from\r\nexpanding into Kamurocho.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "[Didn't I tell you we need to stay\r\nas far away from Kurusu as possible?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "[You know damn well why.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Is something the matter?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "[Do what you must to ensure\r\nthis deal is called off.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "[Come on. We're leaving.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "President Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Please give my regards to your\r\nfather. We must be leaving."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Hold a moment, sir."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Jimmy and I are the only two\r\nprivy to this proposal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "My father, Kurusu,\r\nhas no knowledge of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Oh, and one more thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "[This is not an offer you can refuse.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "You're quite a devil."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "I hadn't realized you were\r\nproficient in our language."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "But I cannot help but wonder,\r\nwhy do you say we cannot refuse?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "The secret of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "I believe you know nothing\r\nof its true nature."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Isn't that right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "It was only a day or so ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Your son and I had a lovely dinner together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "But after a few pours,\r\nhe spoke rather ill of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "He claimed you were blackmailing\r\nKurusu with an empty secret."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "And you fear he may discover that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "He said it several times."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "You...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "Men who talk too much after\r\na drink are easy to manipulate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "Kurusu remains in the dark, though!\r\nIt'll be fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "Do you see why your father forbid\r\nthe Saio Triad from coming to Japan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "It was all to keep Takeru Kurusu from learning\r\nthat he didn't know the truth of the secret."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "That is why he was so intent on limiting\r\nhis interactions with my father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "You needn't worry, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "<font_kind=yakuza_italic>Your</font_kind> secret is safe with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "If my father learned the truth, the <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind>\r\nhe smuggled in would be in grave danger."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "None would be spared."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "And I don't wish that upon them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "Why exactly have you\r\nlured us here to Kamurocho?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "What is your goal in all of this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "In Kamurocho..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||a12_020||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "...The Tojo Clan shall be reborn."
msgstr ""

