msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Isn't that right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "It was only a day or so ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Your son and I had a lovely dinner together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "But after a few pours,\r\nhe spoke rather ill of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "He claimed you were blackmailing\r\nKurusu with an empty secret."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "And you fear he may discover that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "He said it several times."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "You...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Men who talk too much after\r\na drink are easy to manipulate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Kurusu remains in the dark, though!\r\nIt'll be fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Do you see why your father forbid\r\nthe Saio Triad from coming to Japan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "It was all to keep Takeru Kurusu from learning\r\nthat he didn't know the truth of the secret."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "That is why he was so intent on limiting\r\nhis interactions with my father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "You needn't worry, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "<font_kind=yakuza_italic>Your</font_kind> secret is safe with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "If my father learned the truth, the <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind>\r\nhe smuggled in would be in grave danger."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "None would be spared."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "And I don't wish that upon them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "Why exactly have you\r\nlured us here to Kamurocho?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "What is your goal in all of this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "In Kamurocho..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||a12_025||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "...The Tojo Clan shall be reborn."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Tagashira!\r\nWhere are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Aniki! Over here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "This is the spot the code was pointin' to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "The secret's in here.\r\nIt's gotta be!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "It's real freakin' rusty...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Tagashira!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "No way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Hirose?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Secrets are funny things."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "They only stay secret 'cause someone\r\nworks to keep 'em that way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "So it really is you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Patriarch Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "People shouldn't go digging around\r\nin other people's business."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Right, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Cap..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Down there!\r\nThe boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "He's really here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "W-We gotta get down there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "To protect this secret..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "You used Yuta and Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "And..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "You took advantage of Haruka, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Hey, Tagashira!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Sit tight fer a sec."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "I'll explain this whole mess t'you later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "B-Boss..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Yer really the one who's been\r\nprotectin' the secret o' Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "What about Yuta, huh?\r\nYou tried t'turn him into a murderer!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Get outta my way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Tagashira'll find it soon enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "I got no time to waste on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Before I let you go,\r\nthe Hirose Family needs answers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "They need to know why you've\r\nlied to them this whole time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Look."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Just move already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Ain't askin' again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "Answer me first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Hirose!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "I told you to stand the fuck down!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "You want past...\r\nYou'll have to go through me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "You want past...\r\nYou'll have to go through me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||a12_040||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "You want past...\r\nYou'll have to go through me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Patriarch... Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Patriarch... Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "B-Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Wh-What's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Looks like... I failed..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "The hell's goin' on!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Y-You guys!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I pulled this giant lever back there.\r\nThat's what set off this alarm!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Tagashira. This is yer fault?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "The... Yamato...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "That's it!\r\nThe Battleship Yamato!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "That's..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "The secret of Onomichi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Ch-Chairman Kurusu!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "That... isn't the Yamato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "To be more accurate,\r\nit is the Yamato Mark II."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "The most classified military secret in Japan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||a12_060||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Patriarch... Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Y'goddamn punk!\r\nWe ain't gonna let this slide, y'know!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "The hell's this? I didn't realize\r\nthey were hirin' yakuza around here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Right? No bullshit thug can lecture me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "That's enough outta you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Really? Yer gonna pull a gun on a kid?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Go on, just try n' shoot me.\r\nBet y'can't pull the trigger!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Little fuck..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Let's not."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Why you little..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Who the hell're you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "You break into this factory,\r\nbut don't recognize its owner?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "No matter.\r\nJust hand the gun to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Stay back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "My apologies for him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "This only happened because you tried\r\nto punch above your weight, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "However, you have guts for a youngster."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "However, you have guts for a youngster."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "You seem strong as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "What's yer point?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Well... I want you to join me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "I can look after you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I assume you have no family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "And if you continue on with those kids you\r\ncame in with, you won't have a future, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "My friends?\r\nWhat'd you do to them!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Nothing. Just a little slap on the wrist."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "They're gone already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "When asked who led this little operation..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "...They didn't hesitate to pin the whole\r\nplan on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Each one said the same thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "You call those people your friends..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "...But considering their betrayal,\r\nperhaps you should reconsider."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "Is that what real friends would do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "What do you gain from them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "What's the point of it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Discard your former self.\r\nJoin me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "I will make you into a real man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "I will make you into a real man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "However, you have guts for a youngster."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||a12_070||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "I will make you into a real man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "That's it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "That's how I joined the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "But still..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I didn't fit in too good there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I was always fightin' my aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "If I didn't like 'em, I'd hit 'em."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Cause of that, I only ever got sent\r\non the most dangerous missions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Havin' a \"people\" problem?\r\n\"Hirose, get on it.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Havin' a \"people\" problem?\r\n\"Hirose, get on it.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "It was bad, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Kurusu-san took real good care of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "After I came back,\r\nhe'd always treat me to a fancy meal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Kept my pockets full, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "But t'be honest, I was only happy\r\nwhen he approved of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "I woulda done anythin'\r\njust t'hear his praise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "All I could be proud of\r\nwas bein' good at fighting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "But Kurusu-san gave me a reason to live."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "It might've been hard\r\nto say at the time..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "...But I was real grateful fer that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "One night though,\r\nhe called me in fer a meeting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "One night though,\r\nhe called me in fer a meeting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Everythin' changed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Havin' a \"people\" problem?\r\n\"Hirose, get on it.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||a12_080||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "One night though,\r\nhe called me in fer a meeting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Sorry I'm late."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "What's up, Boss?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "How have you been?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Oh, uh... I'm scrapin' by."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "When you look at me, what do you see?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Well, uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "The chairman of the Yomei Alliance.\r\nOh, and the president of Iwami Shipbuilding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "The chairman of the Yomei Alliance.\r\nOh, and the president of Iwami Shipbuilding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Beyond that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "W-Well, you're a really good guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "You've got money and power, too.\r\nThat's it! Yer the perfect man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "You've got money and power, too.\r\nThat's it! Yer the perfect man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "And..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "You're the only guy\r\nI could ever think of as my dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "You're the only guy\r\nI could ever think of as my dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "I adore Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "I adore its natural beauty."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Furthermore, I adore the honest,\r\nhardworking people of this town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Iwami Shipbuilding has\r\nreally grown over time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I've gained more wealth than\r\nmost people can imagine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "However, riches pale in comparison\r\nto the livelihoods we give those people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "That is where the true joy in life lies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "And the Yomei Alliance is no different."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Even kids like you need work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Hiroshima could only benefit by taking you\r\noff the street and into my organization."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "You're right.\r\nI'll never forget what I owe you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "However..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "...Both Iwami Shipbuilding and the Yomei Alliance\r\nmay soon meet their end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Huh!? Wh-Why's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Tell me why!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "There is a great secret hidden in Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "There is a great secret hidden in Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "If it were revealed, it would be\r\nthe end of both of my businesses."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "It would be the end of me as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "It would be the end of me as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "I-I don't get it!\r\nWhat's this big secret?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "That, I cannot say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "That, I cannot say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "Huh? B-But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "Oh. I think I understand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "Someone's blackmailin' you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "Using that secret t'get leverage over you, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "Screw that!\r\nY'don't gotta worry, though!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "I'll take out every last one of 'em!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "Boss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "Tell me, who's blackmailing you?\r\nWhere can I find 'em!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "You are mistaken."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "This isn't a problem a few\r\ndeaths will solve, Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "Huh? Then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "...What can we do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "Boss! I'll do whatever it takes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "Jus' tell me how to fix it!\r\nC'mon, Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||59||||4"
msgid "Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||60||||4"
msgid "I know this may not make much sense,\r\nbut I have a request to make of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||61||||4"
msgid "I know this may not make much sense,\r\nbut I have a request to make of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||62||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||63||||4"
msgid "It involves the secret of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||64||||4"
msgid "The thing that could bring down\r\nIwami Shipbuilding and the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||65||||4"
msgid "And the thing that could rock\r\nthe very foundation of Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "I'd like you to protect it with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "A secret..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||68||||4"
msgid "You want me to protect?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||69||||4"
msgid "Exactly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||70||||4"
msgid "You will never learn the secret itself..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||71||||4"
msgid "...But you will need to risk your life\r\nto guarantee its safety all the same."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||72||||4"
msgid "Until your dying breath."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||73||||4"
msgid "I'll never know what it is,\r\nfor the rest of my life...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||74||||4"
msgid "I'll never know what it is,\r\nfor the rest of my life...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||75||||4"
msgid "Th-That's, uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||76||||4"
msgid "I understand. Protecting an unknown secret\r\nis quite difficult. Perhaps impossible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||77||||4"
msgid "N-Not at all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||78||||4"
msgid "I can do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||79||||4"
msgid "Very well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||80||||4"
msgid "I hope that remains true once\r\nyou see the commitment I expect."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||81||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||82||||4"
msgid "As I demand a great deal from you,\r\nI want to show how invested I am as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||83||||4"
msgid "It is only fair."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||84||||4"
msgid "Don't worry, B-Boss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||85||||4"
msgid "I can keep whatever secret y'have."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||86||||4"
msgid "It's me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||87||||4"
msgid "Yes. As soon as possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||88||||4"
msgid "Hm? Oh, it's you, Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||89||||4"
msgid "Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||90||||4"
msgid "Boss. You called for me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||91||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||92||||4"
msgid "B-Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||93||||4"
msgid "Why!? Why'd y'do that!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||94||||4"
msgid "I needed to prove a point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||95||||4"
msgid "You saw it, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||96||||4"
msgid "And now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||97||||4"
msgid "Will you sell me out to the police?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||98||||4"
msgid "Or can you commit to taking\r\nthis secret to your grave?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||99||||4"
msgid "Or can you commit to taking\r\nthis secret to your grave?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||100||||4"
msgid "Compared to the secret of Onomichi, this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||101||||4"
msgid "This means nothing at all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||102||||4"
msgid "I will do <font_kind=yakuza_italic>anything</font_kind> to protect it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||103||||4"
msgid "I would discard my humanity if need be!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||104||||4"
msgid "Now please."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||105||||4"
msgid "You see what it will take."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||106||||4"
msgid "This town, this company<symbol=em_dash_with_outline> No,\r\nHiroshima requires our protection."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||107||||4"
msgid "This town, this company<symbol=em_dash_with_outline> No,\r\nHiroshima requires our protection."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||108||||4"
msgid "The chairman of the Yomei Alliance.\r\nOh, and the president of Iwami Shipbuilding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||109||||4"
msgid "You've got money and power, too.\r\nThat's it! Yer the perfect man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||110||||4"
msgid "You're the only guy\r\nI could ever think of as my dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||111||||4"
msgid "There is a great secret hidden in Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||112||||4"
msgid "It would be the end of me as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||113||||4"
msgid "That, I cannot say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||114||||4"
msgid "I know this may not make much sense,\r\nbut I have a request to make of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||115||||4"
msgid "I'll never know what it is,\r\nfor the rest of my life...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||116||||4"
msgid "Or can you commit to taking\r\nthis secret to your grave?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||a12_090||cinema_telop||117||||4"
msgid "This town, this company<symbol=em_dash_with_outline> No,\r\nHiroshima requires our protection."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "If you're trying to reach Daidoji-sensei,\r\nI'm afraid he won't be answering."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "If you're trying to reach Daidoji-sensei,\r\nI'm afraid he won't be answering."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "There's no point asking for help now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Tsuneo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "How long have you been here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "The secret is out in the open.\r\nYou're finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "The secret is out in the open.\r\nYou're finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "But things are looking up for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Thanks to you,\r\nDaidoji and I have formed a new contract."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Thanks to you,\r\nDaidoji and I have formed a new contract."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "If you're trying to reach Daidoji-sensei,\r\nI'm afraid he won't be answering."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "The secret is out in the open.\r\nYou're finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||a13_010||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Thanks to you,\r\nDaidoji and I have formed a new contract."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Koshimizu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "The secret of Onomichi is my responsibility now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "The secret of Onomichi is my responsibility now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Along with all the influence Daidoji\r\nbrings to the table. His money, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Stop this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You cannot handle the pressure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "You should have believed in your son..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||a13_020||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "The secret of Onomichi is my responsibility now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "My father, Takeru Kurusu,\r\nhas committed suicide in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "My father, Takeru Kurusu,\r\nhas committed suicide in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Daidoji-sensei."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "The matter of the battleship\r\nin Hiroshima is taken care of."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Nobody will be able to trace it to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Therefore, I have a request."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "You and my late father had an arrangement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I anticipate the same."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Excuse the intrusion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "The one who exposed the ship."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu. Dispose of him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "My time runs short."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "But if you take care of this before my passing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "...You too may earn the name Takeru Kurusu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "I understand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||a13_030||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "My father, Takeru Kurusu,\r\nhas committed suicide in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Apparently Hirose-san's gone now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "But... I won't give up on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "But... I won't give up on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I need you to get up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Please..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Date-san! Hey, wake up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "It's Haruka! Haruka's<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Go get the doctor!\r\nHurry!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||a13_040||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "But... I won't give up on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Ah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Um..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I should probly step out for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "No, it's okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I want you to be here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "I thought when you woke up..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "...The first thing I'd do was lecture you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "I can't believe you just disappeared like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "The kids and I were worried to death."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "I had a lot I wanted to say to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "But now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Now that I see your face alive and well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "...I can't find the words to say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||a13_050||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I'm so sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||a13_060||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hi there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||a13_060||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "You're the fourth chairman, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||a13_060||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "What business do you have here today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||a13_060||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I need to talk to Sugai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||a13_060||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||a13_060||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I can show myself up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||a13_060||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Get out of my way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "You look well, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Hellooo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "What's going on here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "That should be clear, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Someya will be your opponent today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I'm told..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "...You were planning to kill both\r\nmyself and President Iwami, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Well, once you're gone..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "...I will find Haruka Sawamura and her\r\nchild and make sure they're next."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "It doesn't matter if Daidoji dies before then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "This is what happens when you cross us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Your deaths will be a warning to the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Sugai...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Now be a good boy and let Someya kill you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "What happened to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Someya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "What happened, you ask?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "You'll find out in the afterlife."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||a13_070||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Now die!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "You're not the one I'm after."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "It's that sneering asshole behind you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "You'll die if you keep this up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Just stop already!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I'm... not finished yet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Oh dear, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "You have no idea what you've done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Kiyomi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "It seems we'll have to show Someya\r\nthe cost of failing our organization."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "No..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "You took Kiyomi!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Iwami!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I told Someya. If he managed to kill you,\r\nI'd ensure his bitch got home safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately for her,\r\nSomeya has failed to deliver on his promise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately for her,\r\nSomeya has failed to deliver on his promise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Stop it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Please...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "This would never have happened\r\nif you had let Someya kill you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Let her go, Iwami!\r\nShe isn't involved in this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Why don't we trade?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I'll count to three."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "And you... You are going to kill Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "If you do that, I'll let the girl go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "But I should be clear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "I am not known for my patience."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "One."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman.\r\nHe's not messing around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Kill me, I'm begging you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Two."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Time's up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Someya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "No!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Th-The hell's goin' on here!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Kiyomi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Our daughter..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "Hiromi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "I never raised a hand to her...\r\nNot even once..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "I treated her like a princess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "Believe me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "What a tender moment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "That was a rather touching\r\ndisplay of familial love."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "Someya-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "What are you doing!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "Well, he said time's up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "Y'know what that means."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "Kiyo-chan..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "N-No..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "This ain't happenin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "Nagumo-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "Hiromi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "Our daughter... Please..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "I beg of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||59||||4"
msgid "What're y'talkin' about!?\r\nYer gonna be fine!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||60||||4"
msgid "We can still save ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||61||||4"
msgid "Promise me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||62||||4"
msgid "Promise me... You'll take care of her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||63||||4"
msgid "I need to hear it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||64||||4"
msgid "Nagumo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||65||||4"
msgid "I'll do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "She's gonna be jus' fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "Y'can rest easy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||a13_080||cinema_telop||68||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately for her,\r\nSomeya has failed to deliver on his promise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "W-Wait, please..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "I've waited long enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "People are expecting you in hell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "You're nothing. Just a pathetic fool who\r\ndrags civilians into yakuza conflicts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Do it, Sugai!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Kill the girl and the stupid kid!\r\nEnd them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Nagumo! Damn it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Die!\r\nJust die already!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Haruka... and Haruto..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Are they okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Yeah! They're just fine, Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Please..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Please take care of them, Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "You can't die on us like this! Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Goddammit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "You'll pay fer what y'did to Kiryu-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "So this is where the dream ends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Get an ambulance down to the shipyard!\r\nAs fast as y'can!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "I'm glad... you're safe... Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "No..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Don't look so satisfied about this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "You can't leave me, Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "You can't give up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Yuta... and Haruto..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Make them... happy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||a13_110||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Knowin' Kiyo-chan..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "...I'm sure she was always thinkin' about ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Y'were jus' three when\r\ny'got separated, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "D'ya remember her?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Yer mom, I mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Only from pictures."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "But... my dad always talked about her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Someya did?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "He said she didn't like his job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "That's why she had to leave him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "My dad..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "He blamed himself for driving her away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "I getcha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "But still, y'can't be too sad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Yer daddy raised ya up fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Kiyo-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Still think it's crazy she made it out okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Was Koshimizu protectin' her or somethin'?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Seems the gun he had on Kiyomi-san\r\nwas loaded with blanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I mean, he had just watched\r\nSomeya kill himself to save her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Musta made him consider a better way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "If we were livin' in a different world, maybe\r\nhe wouldn'ta gotten mixed up in all this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "He was probly sick o' bein' Iwami's lap dog.\r\nWho wouldn't be, t'be honest?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Why he did it doesn't matter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "It's thanks to him that Kiyomi-san's still alive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Y'gotta feel fer Cap, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "His rival fer Kiyomi-san's heart\r\nkilled himself t'save her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Ain't exactly a level he can compete on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "But fer now, he's gotta focus\r\non rebuildin' the Hirose Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "You gotta help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Y'can do it, Tagashira."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "You too, Matsunaga-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Take care o' yerselves down in Okinawa, Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "Haruka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "And you too, Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "As fer Kiryu-aniki..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "It's a damn shame."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "I'm still havin' trouble processin' it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "He was a force to be reckoned with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "But for Haruto..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "I think that when he gets bigger, he'll\r\nremember the time he spent with Uncle Kaz."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "I will too.\r\nI could never forget him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz showed me so much warmth in life..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||a13_120||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "...And now, \r\nI have to do the same for him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Ya must be tired just getting outta the slammer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "We've been waitin' for you, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "You heard, didn't ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "We're on the brink of war\r\nwith the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Everyone's chompin' at the bit to\r\nget revenge for the fourth chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Ain't no halting that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Can't say I disagree, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "So what's yer plan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Sixth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Takeru Kurusu is dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "His son Tsuneo is behind bars now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "And this Koshimizu guy has yet to take\r\nfull control of the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "And this Koshimizu guy has yet to take\r\nfull control of the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "So? You sayin' we strike Hiroshima\r\nwhile the iron's hot?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Hiroshima's gonna expect us\r\nto come knockin' sooner or later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Sooner makes a shitton more sense to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||a13_130||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "And this Koshimizu guy has yet to take\r\nfull control of the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "I have a long list of regrets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "I have no business saying it, but,\r\nI considered myself your father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I have no business saying it, but,\r\nI considered myself your father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "The things I should have told you over\r\nthe years have piled up like a mountain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I failed you, though.\r\nSo much has been left unsaid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "I failed you, though.\r\nSo much has been left unsaid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "In the past few weeks, I've seen so\r\nmany different kinds of relationships."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Different types of parents."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "I saw a parent bound by customs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Another who never loved his son...\r\nand only realized after it was too late."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Children who, above all, wanted to prove themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Show their parents they were capable.\r\nProve that they deserved their love."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "So much grief came of it, the rift between\r\nparent and child. I saw it firsthand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Did these families have no faith in their bonds?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "That wasn't it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "They had absolute faith in those bonds."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Even in this harsh reality, they tried to affirm\r\ntheir bonds. Labored, agonized over them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "But... that wasn't the answer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "They simply didn't spend enough time together\r\nas a family. And it ruined them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "If you ask me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "...Nothing is more vital than time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "To that end, I think we made\r\nthe same mistakes they did."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "I never expected to become\r\nthe Tojo Clan's fourth chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Then I tapped you to\r\nbecome the sixth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Daigo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "I considered you my son,\r\nbut I never thought to actually stand by your side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "It was easy to say I had faith in your judgment.\r\nTo say I entrusted everything to Daigo Dojima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "But that wasn't enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Instead of cherishing our time together,\r\nI threw it all away. Rejected our bond."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Instead of facing my past, I ran.\r\nAnd ran from you as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Thinking about the parents I've met..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "I don't even have the words."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "I don't have the right to call myself a\r\nfather to either you or the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "So, by the time you read this letter,\r\nI may already be gone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "But please, don't try to avenge me\r\nas a son would his father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "My life isn't worth that much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "That is my final request of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Daigo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "I have no business saying it, but,\r\nI considered myself your father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||a13_140||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "I failed you, though.\r\nSo much has been left unsaid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "My father has made a request of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "I will honor his wishes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "We will not march on Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Instead, I will approach the Yomei Alliance\r\nabout a pact. One that sees us as equals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-chan, always thinkin' ten steps ahead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "This letter revealed something to me<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Just how great a man my father was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Guess ya did alright after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||a13_150||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Fire!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Little Asia's up in flames!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Several fires were reported all around\r\nLittle Asia at roughly the same time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Do you think it's arson?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Fire department better be on the way.\r\nHow's the evac going?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Well, sir!\r\nIt's spreading quickly though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "What a mess..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Little Asia's gonna burn to cinders."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What do you think?\r\nQuite a view, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "These flames should serve as\r\nproof of our dedication to the cause."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Gentlemen, lasting prosperity is\r\nnow within arm's reach."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||a01_079||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Shall we toast to that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "I was scared outta my mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "It felt kinda weird, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I'd just watched a man get murdered."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I was so afraid of seein' that again,\r\nit didn't matter <font_kind=yakuza_italic>what</font_kind> the secret was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I was so afraid of seein' that again,\r\nit didn't matter <font_kind=yakuza_italic>what</font_kind> the secret was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "But then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "To protect that secret..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "...You became a murderer yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "It was jus' part of the job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "That ain't true, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "When the boss bowed to me,\r\nI felt important."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Important to Kurusu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "To Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "To Japan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "I was just some little shit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "...But it felt like I had\r\nthe potential to be someone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "That was my driving force."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Never underestimate an idiot!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "But y'already know that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Or maybe not?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Hirose has been exemplary.\r\nHe carried out my orders without fail."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Hirose has been exemplary.\r\nHe carried out my orders without fail."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "His beloved aniki,\r\nleaders of the Yomei Alliance..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "They all fell by his hand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "The secret of Onomichi was safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Protected by the deaths of\r\nmy subordinates... and my friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "I hope you understand what you've done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "You have rendered their deaths meaningless."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "And for this heinous crime..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "...You too must die."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Whaddya think yer doin', boss?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Finish it, Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "You must kill each and every one of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Leave not a single soul in this world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Boss..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "Y'can't do this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "Why do you hesitate?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Hirose!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "I can't do it, Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "Look!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "Nagumo's..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "Hey, you don't have to die."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "You probably don't get all\r\nthis secret business anyway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "Just step aside, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "Boss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "Can you at least lemme spare<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "Compromise is unacceptable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "Hirose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "There is another thing\r\nI've never told you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "It concerns the order Daidoji gave me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "What he really wanted for the battleship..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "...Was its destruction."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "He never suggested that I murder\r\nthe others who knew about the secret."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||59||||4"
msgid "I did."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||60||||4"
msgid "What the hell!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||61||||4"
msgid "Without the battleship,\r\nI would have lost my leverage over Daidoji."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||62||||4"
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||63||||4"
msgid "Let him go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||64||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||65||||4"
msgid "He's already a dead man walking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "Wow... It's incredible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "That's it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||68||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||69||||4"
msgid "Y'know..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||70||||4"
msgid "I always wondered what\r\nthe secret of Onomichi was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||71||||4"
msgid "I'm glad I got t'see it before I die."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||72||||4"
msgid "Thanks for that, boys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||73||||4"
msgid "Patriarch..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||74||||4"
msgid "Nagumo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||75||||4"
msgid "Wh-What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||76||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||77||||4"
msgid "Boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||78||||4"
msgid "Truth is, I was hopin' you guys\r\nwould be the ones t'kill me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||79||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whaddya mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||80||||4"
msgid "If y'remember, yer dads were my aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||81||||4"
msgid "We know that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||82||||4"
msgid "That's why y'took us in!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||83||||4"
msgid "Not really..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||84||||4"
msgid "They..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||85||||4"
msgid "I had to do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||86||||4"
msgid "I had to..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||87||||4"
msgid "N-No way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||88||||4"
msgid "Boss, you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||89||||4"
msgid "You killed our dads...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||90||||4"
msgid "I'm... sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||92||||4"
msgid "Hirose-san!!!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||93||||4"
msgid "I was so afraid of seein' that again,\r\nit didn't matter <font_kind=yakuza_italic>what</font_kind> the secret was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||94||||4"
msgid "Hirose has been exemplary.\r\nHe carried out my orders without fail."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||a12_100||cinema_telop||96||||4"
msgid "They knew the secret of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "You are the Dragon of Dojima, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "What could a man like yourself have wanted\r\nout in Onomichi? I'm very much intrigued."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "[I doubt he knows the truth about Onomichi.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "[The secret that town holds\r\ncan never be revealed.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "So what exactly did Lo say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "It was basically this:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "There's a secret hidden in Onomichi\r\nthat can't be discovered, no matter what."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "What could he be referring to?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||a07_040||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "The secret of Onomichi...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Onomichi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Out there lies a secret which\r\nmust never see the light of day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "To this end, Yuta Usami's failure\r\nto end Lo is a thorn in our side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Lo will attempt to\r\nreveal the truth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "70 years ago..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "We really gonna let all that\r\nwork amount to nothing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Protecting the secret of Onomichi has required\r\nsacrifices from our very own flesh and blood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Protecting the secret of Onomichi has required\r\nsacrifices from our very own flesh and blood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Isn't that right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "But now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "...A new sacrifice must be made\r\nin order to keep it hidden."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Can I put my faith in you, Hirose?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||a12_010||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Protecting the secret of Onomichi has required\r\nsacrifices from our very own flesh and blood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Iwami Shipbuilding,\r\nat their Onomichi headquarters..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Iwami Shipbuilding,\r\nat their Onomichi headquarters..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "...today held a funeral for their former\r\nchairman, Heizo Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "After the surfacing of the mysterious\r\nship dubbed the Yamato Mark II..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "...Chairman Iwami unexpectedly committed\r\nsuicide in his home with a small handgun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Yuta-kun?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "At this time of great stress, the world has its eyes on\r\nthe company's heir, President Tsuneo Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Impressive, Dragon of Dojima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "You've done quite well!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "We've been expecting you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "You are to be the entertainment for\r\nthe succession of our second Takeru Kurusu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "You'll need a third Kurusu soon enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Y'know..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "I actually kinda liked that Someya guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "That cute little mama, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "She looked so pretty before she died."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Koshimizu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Hiroshima is my home turf.\r\nYou have no hope of winning here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Winning doesn't matter anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "All I care about now is ending the two of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "That's all I came to do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "We weren't expectin' t'leave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Y'hear!? Y'gonna fight us,\r\ny'better be ready t'die!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||a13_090||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "Iwami Shipbuilding,\r\nat their Onomichi headquarters..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "W-Wait..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Shall we put an end to this, Sugai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "Let's."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Haruka!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "N' the baby, too?\r\nTh-The hell's goin' on!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Remember Honjo, that Tokyo detective?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "This afternoon, he received a special order,\r\ndirect from his superiors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "This afternoon, he received a special order,\r\ndirect from his superiors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "He was told to monitor Detective Date\r\nand rescue the girl and her child."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "After all, they were being illegally imprisoned."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Honjo? What are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Date-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "How could you do something like this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?\r\nWho's giving the order?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Date-san, why!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "You've been caught in the act of\r\nillegal confinement. Don't try to resist."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "You've got it wrong, Honjo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "This is exactly what the people\r\nwho are after Haruka want!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Someone must have paid off the chief!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I assure you, my orders came through\r\nthe appropriate channels."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Take them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "You bastard!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "Date-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "If you want the girl and\r\nher child to leave here alive..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "...Don't move a goddamn muscle!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "I'll kill you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Not so fast!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "You've been a thorn in the Tojo Clan\r\nand the Yomei Alliance for too long!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "What do you take us for!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "You...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "And the sixth chairman...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Always...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "Looking down on me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Dieee!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Step aside, Sugai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "It would take far too long\r\nfor you to kill him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "My father never understood my true nature."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "Compared to him, I'm far more ambitious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "My thirst for power is unquenchable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "All my life he pushed me toward an honest career,\r\nbut that only led me to resent him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "All my life he pushed me toward an honest career,\r\nbut that only led me to resent him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "Restricting a child's mobility only\r\npushes them toward rebellion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "This is where I belong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "With the talent I possess, my father\r\nshould have realized that years ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "The legendary yakuza name Takeru Kurusu..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "...is rightfully mine!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "I'll give you ten seconds to stand up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "The girl is dead if you don't."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "Oh dear.\r\nStruggling, are we?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "Behind ya, fucker!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "I-Iwami-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "Aniki! Cap!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "We'll keep Haruka and Haruto safe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||59||||4"
msgid "Yer gonna get a nice lecture about\r\ngoin' off on yer own later, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||60||||4"
msgid "Both o' ya... On yer feet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||61||||4"
msgid "Y'can do it, Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||62||||4"
msgid "Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||63||||4"
msgid "Stand up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||64||||4"
msgid "You're supposed to be dead!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||65||||4"
msgid "You..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "You're about to understand..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "Just who you picked a fight with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||68||||4"
msgid "Don't fuck with me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||69||||4"
msgid "Iwami-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||70||||4"
msgid "Eyes on me, y'piece of shit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||71||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||72||||4"
msgid "Now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||73||||4"
msgid "There's nothing holding me back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||74||||4"
msgid "If I'm going down..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||75||||4"
msgid "...I'm dragging you to hell with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||76||||4"
msgid "Little baby Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||77||||4"
msgid "How dare you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||78||||4"
msgid "You won't leave here alive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||79||||4"
msgid "This is the end of the line."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||80||||4"
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||81||||4"
msgid "This afternoon, he received a special order,\r\ndirect from his superiors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||a13_100||cinema_telop||82||||4"
msgid "All my life he pushed me toward an honest career,\r\nbut that only led me to resent him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Sky Finance is gonna be making\r\na comeback just a couple floors up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Thought it'd only be right to stop in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "I heard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "Congrats on that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "Anyway..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "I've been thinking about Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Date-san, you really saw the body?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Is he really gone?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Yeah he is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "C'mon, one more time, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "You can do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "Come to us, Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "You can do it, Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "Oh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "Ohhh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "You're doing it, Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "Ahh, so close!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Only one guy can confirm Kiryu-san's death,\r\nand that's you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "Only one guy can confirm Kiryu-san's death,\r\nand that's you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "Then they cremate the body like they're\r\n<font_kind=yakuza_italic>trying</font_kind> to be fishy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "Kiryu has no living relatives."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "There was no reason to keep his body intact."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I only got to see him because of my connections."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "That the line you're going to feed me every time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Someday, once things are a little different..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "...I hope you'll tell me what really happened."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "Date-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Are you awake?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "I have some news."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "I've just heard that Minoru Daidoji-sensei\r\npassed away in his sleep yesterday."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "So? Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "I am a politician, mentored in the art of\r\ngoverning over the years by Daidoji-sensei."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "This Onomichi incident has caused quite a stir.\r\nIt's been all over the news."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Right around election season, as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "You've given us a massive headache."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "We're putting out fires left and right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||40||||4"
msgid "But I suppose all fires burn out in time.\r\nWe simply have to wait."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||41||||4"
msgid "It's also possible for a small spark to\r\nerupt into a swirling inferno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||42||||4"
msgid "The Yamato Mark II.\r\nTakeru Kurusu. Tsuneo Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||43||||4"
msgid "We cannot allow Daidoji-sensei's connections\r\nto these blights to come out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||44||||4"
msgid "Is that clear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||45||||4"
msgid "If you spoke to the media of this, Daidoji-sensei's\r\nreputation would be irreparably damaged."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||46||||4"
msgid "If you spoke to the media of this, Daidoji-sensei's\r\nreputation would be irreparably damaged."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||47||||4"
msgid "Beyond that, inquiries would begin into\r\nthe past actions of anyone involved with him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||48||||4"
msgid "In other words, the politicians steering\r\nour country would come under fire."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||49||||4"
msgid "Do you understand?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||50||||4"
msgid "Then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||51||||4"
msgid "...You're one of those politicians?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||52||||4"
msgid "And, this would be hush money."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||53||||4"
msgid "I've done a great deal of research on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||54||||4"
msgid "Do you have a soft spot for orphanages?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||55||||4"
msgid "You certainly need money to run one.\r\nI'm a sympathetic man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||56||||4"
msgid "And I could never threaten a man in a hospital bed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||57||||4"
msgid "All you need to do is accept this money,\r\nand promise you'll keep our secrets safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||58||||4"
msgid "That is all we ask."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||59||||4"
msgid "Not happening."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||60||||4"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||61||||4"
msgid "If you want me to keep your secrets..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||62||||4"
msgid "...I have conditions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||63||||4"
msgid "E-Excuse me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||64||||4"
msgid "Do you know who you're talking to!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||65||||4"
msgid "First, I need Daigo Dojima out of prison."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||66||||4"
msgid "If he stays locked away, Hiroshima\r\nwill be overrun by a yakuza war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||67||||4"
msgid "That would be some fire to put out,\r\nwouldn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||68||||4"
msgid "But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||69||||4"
msgid "You ingrate! Do you understand\r\nthe situation you're in right now!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||70||||4"
msgid "If you don't accept my conditions,\r\nthere's no deal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||71||||4"
msgid "You can live the rest of your life in fear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||72||||4"
msgid "Are all yakuza this stupid?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||73||||4"
msgid "You shouldn't take me so lightly.\r\nDon't you value your life?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||74||||4"
msgid "And what about your family? Your friends?\r\nWho knows how they would end up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||75||||4"
msgid "Try me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||76||||4"
msgid "You say you did the research?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||77||||4"
msgid "Then you know what happens\r\nwhen people hurt my family?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||78||||4"
msgid "You want that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||79||||4"
msgid "But then, how can you guarantee you'll\r\nkeep our secret safe? What will you do!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||80||||4"
msgid "I'll die for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||81||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||82||||4"
msgid "Use your influence. Make the hospital\r\nissue a death certificate for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||83||||4"
msgid "Nobody will ever hear from me again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||84||||4"
msgid "That's my final condition."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||85||||4"
msgid "What're you doing, Kiryu!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||86||||4"
msgid "You heard me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||87||||4"
msgid "I'm going to disappear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||88||||4"
msgid "Tell everyone you ID'd my corpse.\r\nThey need to believe I'm really dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||89||||4"
msgid "What do you say?\r\nThis man can be our witness."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||90||||4"
msgid "Do you accept?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||91||||4"
msgid "Hey, that's enough!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||92||||4"
msgid "Don't you get it!? If you do this,\r\nyou'll never see Haruka or Haruto again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||93||||4"
msgid "You're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||94||||4"
msgid "Very well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||95||||4"
msgid "I accept your conditions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||96||||4"
msgid "Dammit! Why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||97||||4"
msgid "Why are you always so reckless!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||98||||4"
msgid "Haruka, Haruto, and the others..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||99||||4"
msgid "They mean more than the world to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||100||||4"
msgid "If it means keeping them safe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||101||||4"
msgid "...I'd gladly give my life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||102||||4"
msgid "Man..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||103||||4"
msgid "I'm really sticking my neck out for him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||104||||4"
msgid "Stubborn sonuvabitch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||105||||4"
msgid "All right!\r\nThat's it, Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||106||||4"
msgid "Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||107||||4"
msgid "You're doing it!\r\nLet's go, Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||108||||4"
msgid "Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||109||||4"
msgid "Ah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||110||||4"
msgid "Try again, Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||111||||4"
msgid "You can do this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||112||||4"
msgid "Yes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||113||||4"
msgid "Let's go, Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||114||||4"
msgid "You can do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||115||||4"
msgid "You can do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||116||||4"
msgid "You can do this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||117||||4"
msgid "Hang in there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||128||||4"
msgid "Only one guy can confirm Kiryu-san's death,\r\nand that's you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||a13_160||cinema_telop||129||||4"
msgid "If you spoke to the media of this, Daidoji-sensei's\r\nreputation would be irreparably damaged."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "Hey..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "Are you sure about this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "I mean, don't you think\r\nit's almost time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "No, he should be fine for now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "I just want to enjoy my drink\r\nfor a little longer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "You."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Outside, now, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||8||||4"
msgid "Thought I told you I don't wanna\r\nsee yer sorry ass in here again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||9||||4"
msgid "Could you at least try to be\r\na little polite to my customers?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||10||||4"
msgid "But I been coming 'round yer\r\nplace way longer than this guy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||11||||4"
msgid "Y'gonna pick him over me?\r\nReally?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||12||||4"
msgid "Yer headin' fer\r\na real whuppin' this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||13||||4"
msgid "Well!? Get on out there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||14||||4"
msgid "I ain't lettin' you ignore me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||15||||4"
msgid "Hey, Nagumo-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||16||||4"
msgid "O-Oh, uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||17||||4"
msgid "I'll pay you back later, 'kay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||18||||4"
msgid "Sorry 'bout that, Kiyo-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||19||||4"
msgid "I won't be long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||20||||4"
msgid "Like hell you won't."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||21||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna make sure\r\ny'get gone fer good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||22||||4"
msgid "I'll swing by some other time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||23||||4"
msgid "See ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||24||||4"
msgid "Y'ready to tussle? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||25||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna teach ya good, punks\r\nwho mess with me don't get off easy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||26||||4"
msgid "Best start prayin' now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||27||||4"
msgid "Truth is, y'just made a fool outta me\r\nin front of the woman I love..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||28||||4"
msgid "How d'you reckon that feels?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||29||||4"
msgid "The Hiroshima yakuza don't take kindly\r\nto trash like you, y'hear me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||30||||4"
msgid "Givin' me all that high n' mighty bull..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||31||||4"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||32||||4"
msgid "Whaddya want!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||33||||4"
msgid "Can we get this over with?\r\nI'm on a schedule here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||34||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah?\r\nY'really itchin' to die that bad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||35||||4"
msgid "Just hurry up and fight me already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||36||||4"
msgid "It's really gonna mess up my plans if I\r\nhave to listen to any more of this hot air."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||37||||4"
msgid "Well y'don't gotta worry then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||38||||4"
msgid "Cause startin' now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||a01_015||cinema_telop||39||||4"
msgid "...All yer plans are canceled!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||a11_015||cinema_telop||1||||4"
msgid "[You know who I am, right?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||a11_015||cinema_telop||2||||4"
msgid "[I'm here for my father.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||a11_015||cinema_telop||3||||4"
msgid "[If he's not here...\r\nI can wait inside.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||a11_015||cinema_telop||4||||4"
msgid "[Spread your arms.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||a11_015||cinema_telop||5||||4"
msgid "[Hands off.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||a11_015||cinema_telop||6||||4"
msgid "[I need more booze than\r\nthis to talk to that bastard.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||a11_015||cinema_telop||7||||4"
msgid "Yo, bio-dad.\r\nCare for a drink?"
msgstr ""

